hadiths[267]{hadithnumber,text}:
1570,"Saleh bin kaisaan ne Urwa-bin-Zubair se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha, safar aur hazar ( muqeem honey ki haalat ( mein Namaz 2-2 rakaat farz ki gaee thi, phir safar ki Namaz ( pehli haalat par) qaaim rakhi gaee aur hazar ki Namaz mein izafa kar diya gaya."
1571,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha, mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne hadis bayan ki, ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : jab Allah Taala ne Namaz farz ki to wo 2 rakaat farz ki, phir hazar ki sura mein usey mukammal kar diya aur safar ki Namaz ko pahley fareezey par qaaim rakha gaya."
1572,"ibne-Uena ne Zohri se unhon-ne Urwa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke shuruaat mein Namaz 2 rakaat farz ki gaee, phir safar ki Namaz , (usi haalat mein) bar-qaraar rakhi gaee aur hazar ki Namaz mukammal kar di gaee. imam Zohri ne kaha : maine Urwa se puchha Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ka mauqif kya hai. wo safar mein poori Namaz ( kyon ( padhti thin ? unhon-ne kaha : unhon-ne iska aik mafhoom ley liya hai jis tarah Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne liya."
1573,"Abdullah-bin-Idris ne ibne-Juraij se, unhon-ne ibne-abi Ammar se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Babehi se aur unhon-ne Yala bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki : kaha : maine Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha (ke Allah Taala ka farman hai) agar tumhen khof ho ke kaafir tumhen fitney mein daal dengey to tum par koi harj nahi hai ke tum Namaz qasr kar lo ab to log amn mein hain ( phir qasr kyon kartey hain? to unhon-ne jawab diya mujhey bhi is baat par tajjub hua tha jis par tumhen tajjub hua hai. to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske barey mein sawal kya tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (ye ( sadqa ( riaayat ( hai jo Allah Taala ne tum par kya hai is liye tum iska sadqa qabool karo."
1574,"Yahya ne ibne-Juraij se pichhli sanad ke sath Hazrat Yala bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha ! maine Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se arz ki. (Baqiya riwayat ( ibne-Idrees ki hadis ki tarah hai."
1575,"abu-Awana ne Bukair bin Akhnas se, unhon-ne Mujahid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Allah Taala ne tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zaban se Namaz farz ki, hazar (jab muqeem hon ( mein char rakatein , safar mein 2 rakatein aur khof ( jang ( mein (Imam ke saath) aik rakaat ( phir uski imamat ke baghair aik rakaat ( ."
1576,"Ayub bin Aaiz Tai ne Bukair bin Akhnas se, unhon-ne Mujahid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, kaha ! be-shak Allah Taala ne tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zaban se Namaz farz ki, musaafir par 2 rakatein , muqeem par char aur) jang ke) khof ke aalim mein (Imam ki iqtida (pairvi) mein) aik rakaat (aur iqtida (pairvi) ke baghair aik rakaat ( ."
1577,"Shoba ne kaha : maine Qatada se suna, wo Musa bin Salma Hazli ( Basri) se hadis bayan kar rahe they. kaha : maine Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : jab main Makka mein hun aur imam ke sath Namaz na padhun to phir kaisey Namaz padhun? to unhon-ne jawab diya : 2 rakatein, (yahi) abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sunnat hai."
1578,"( Shoba ki bajaey) Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba aur Muaz bin Hisham ne apne walid ke waastey se Qatada se, usi mazkura (uper zikr) sanad ke sath isi tarah ( hadis bayan ki) ."
1579,"Esa bin Hafs bin Aasim bin umr bin-Khattab ne apne walid ( Hafs ( se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Makka ke rastey mein Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath safar kya, unhon-ne hamein Zohar ki Namaz 2 rakatein padhai , phir wo aur ham aagey badhey aur apni qiyam gaah par aaey aur baith gaey, ham bhi unke sath baith gaey. phir achcha unki tawajjoh us taraf hui jahan unhon-ne Namaz padhi thi, unhon-ne ( wahan ( logon ko qiyam ki haalat mein dekha unhon-ne poochha, ye log kya kar rahe hain? maine kaha : sunnatein padh rahe hain. unhon-ne kaha : agar mujhey sunnatein padhni hotin to main Namaz ( bhi) poori karta ( qasr na karta ( bhatijey ! main safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath raha aap ne 2 rakaat se zayed Namaz na padhi yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne aapko apne paas bula liya aur main Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath raha unhon-ne bhi 2 rakaat se zyada Namaz na padhi yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne unhein bhi bula liya, aur main Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath raha, unhon-ne bhi 2 rakaat Namaz se zayed na padhi. yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne unhein bhi bula liya. phir main Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath raha unhon-ne bhi 2 se zayed rakatein nahi padhein, yahan tak ke Allah ne unhein bula liya aur Allah Taala ka farman hai : be-shak tumharey liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ke amal ( mein behtreen namoona hai."
1580,"Umar-bin-Muhammad ne Hafs bin Aasim se riwayat ki, kaha : main bimar hua to ( Abdullah (bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) meri iyaadat karne aaey kaha : maine unse safar mein sunnatein padhney ke barey mein sawal kya. unhon-ne kaha : main safar ke doran Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath raha hun. maine nahi dekha ke aap sunnatein padhtey hon, aur agar mujhey sunnatein padhni hotin to main Namaz hi poori padhta . Allah Taala ne farmaya hai : be-shak tumharey liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ke amal ( mein behtreen namoona hai."
1581,abu-Qilaba ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Madina mein Zohar ki char rakaat padhein aur zul-Hulaifa mein Asr ki 2 rakatein padhein.
1582,Muhammad-bin-Munkadir aur Ibrahim-bin-Maisra donon ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna keh rahe they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Madina mein Zohar ki char rakaat padhein aur aap ke sath zul-Hulaifa mein Asr ki 2 rakatein padhin.
1583,"Shoba ne Yahya bin Yazeed Hunai se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se Namaz qasr karne ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab teen mail ya teen farsakh ki masafat par nikaltey . masafat ke barey mein shak karne waley Shoba hain. to 2 rakaat Namaz padhtey ."
1584,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne hadis bayan ki kaha : hamein Shoba ne Yazeed bin Khumair se hadis sunai. unhon-ne Habib bin Ubaid se unhon-ne Jubair-bin-Nufair se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Shurehbil bin-Simt ( al-Kindi (ke sath aik basti ko gaya jo satrah ya atthara mail ke faasley par thi to unhon-ne 2 rakaat Namaz padhi, maine unse poochha, unhon-ne jawab diya : maine Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko zul-Hulaifa mein 2 rakaat padhtey dekha hai, to maine un (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu)) se poochha, unhon-ne jawab diya : main isi tarah karta hun jis tarah maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kartey dekha hai."
1585,Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath ye hadis bayan ki aur kaha : ibne- Samt se riwayat hai aur unhon-ne Shurehbil ka naam liya aur kaha : wo teiswin ki (Dumin) naam ke jagah par pahunchey jo atthara mail ke faasley par thi (aur wahan Namaz qasr padhi ( .
1586,"Hushaim ne Yahya bin abi Ishaq se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Madina se Makka janey ke liye nikley to aap 2 rakaat Namaz padhtey rahe yahan tak ke Madina wapas pahunch gaey. rawi ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : aap Makka kitna arsa tahrey ? unhon-ne jawab diya : das din (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par Makka aa kar khud Makka , Mina , Arafaat aur Muzdalfa mukhtalif maqamat par das din guzaarey .)"
1587,abu-Awana aur (Ismail ( ibne-Ulaih ne Yahya bin abi Ishaq se unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Hushaim ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
1588,"Shoba ne kaha : mujhey Yahya bin abi Ishaq ne hadis sunai, kaha : maine Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo bayan kartey they ke ham Haj ke liye Madina se chaley. padhi. phir uper zikr ki gaee riwayat bayan ki."
1589,"( Sufiyan ( Sory ne Yahya bin abi Ishaq se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi pichhli hadis ki tarah hadis riwayat ki aur (is mein) Haj ka tazkira nahi kya."
1590,"Amr-bin-Haris ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Salim bin-Abdullah (bin umr ( se, unhon-ne apne walid (Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Mina aur dusri jaghon, yani uske aas-paas aur (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad) Hazrat Abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne musaafir ki namaz, yani 2 rakatein padhein aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi apni khilafat ke shuruati saalon mein 2 rakatein padhin, baad mein poori char padhney lagey."
1591,"Auzai aur Mamar ne (apni apni sanad se riwayat kartey huey) Zohri se baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath yahi hadis riwayat ki, unhon-ne Mina mein kaha aur dusri jaghon ke alfaz nahi kahey ."
1592,"abu-Usama ne kaha : hamein Ubaidullah-bin-Umar ne Naafe se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Mina mein 2 rakatein padhin, aap ke baad Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke baad Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni khilafat ke shuruati saalon mein (2 rakatein padhin) phir Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne iske baad char rakatein padhin. isliye Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) jab imam ke sath Namaz padhtey to char rakaat padhtey aur jab akeley padhtey to 2 rakatein padhtey ."
1593,"Yahya qattan, ibne-abi-Zayda aur Aqba bin Khalid ne Ubaidullah se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah riwayat ki."
1594,"Ubaidullah-bin-Muaz ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mere walid ne hamein hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Khubaib bin Abdur-Rehman se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hafs bin Aasim se suna, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Abu-Bakar , umr , aur Usman , rizwaanullahi-anhum ajmaeen ne (pahley ( aath (8) saal ya kaha : chh saal . Mina mein musaafir wali Namaz padhi. Hafs ne kaha : ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Mina mein 2 rakaat Namaz padhtey they. phir apne bistar par aa jatey they. maine kaha : chacha jaan ! agar aap farz Namaz ke baad 2 sunnatein bhi padh liya karein ! to unhon-ne kaha : agar main aisa karun to ( maano ( poori Namaz padhun."
1595,Khalid-bin Haris aur Abdus-Samad ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne (baqi bachi) isi sanad ke sath yahi riwayat bayan ki lekin un donon ne us hadis mein Mina mein ke alfaz nahi kahey lekin donon ne ye kaha : aap ne safar mein Namaz padhi.
1596,"abdul-Wahid ne Aamash se hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Ibrahim ne hadis sunai, kaha : maine Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed se suna, keh rahe they : Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Mina mein char rakaat padhaaein , ye baat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ko batai gaee to unhon-ne  انا للہ وانا الیہ راجعون padha phir kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Mina mein 2 rakaat Namaz padhi, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Mina mein 2 rakaat Namaz padhi aur umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Mina mein 2 rakaat Namaz padhi, kash! ! mere naseeb mein char rakaat ke badley sharf qabooliyat hasil karne wali 2 rakatein hon."
1597,"abu-Muawiya , Jarir aur Esa sab ne ( mukhtalif sanadon se riwayat kartey huey) Aamash se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis bayan ki hai."
1598,"abu-Ahwas ne Abu-Ishaq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Harisa bin Wahab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Mina mein 2 rakaat Namaz padhi, (jab ( log sabse zyada amn mein aur Kasir tadaad mein they. (ye Allah ki rukhsat ko qabool karne ka mamla tha, khof , bd-amni ya jang ka mamla na tha.)"
1599,"Zuhair ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Abu-Ishaq ne hadis sunai, kaha, mujh se Harisa bin Wahab Khuzai (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki kaha : maine Mina main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein Namaz padhi jabke log ( tadaad mein) jitney zyada ho saktey they ( maujood they) aap ne Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par 2 rakaat Namaz padhai. Imam Muslim (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Harisa bin Wahab Khuzai (Raziallahu anhu) maan ( Muleka binte- jarwal Khuzaia) ki taraf se Ubaidullah-bin-Umar bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke bhai they."
1600,Imam Malik ne Naafe se riwayat ki ke ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne sardi aur hawa wali aik raat azan kahi aur uske aakhir mein kaha : ( أَلَا صَلُّوا فِي الرِّحَالِ ( suno ! (apne ( thikanon mein Namaz padh lo. phir kaha ke jab raat sard aur barish wali hoti to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) muazzan ko hukm detey ke wo kahey ( أَلَا صَلُّوا فِي الرِّحَالِ ( suno ! (apne ( thikaanon par Namaz padh lo.
1601,"Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bin Numer ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey mere walid ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne hadis sunai, kaha : mujhey Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne sardi, hawa aur barish wali aik raat mein azan di aur azan ke aakhir mein kaha : suno! apne thikanon mein Namaz padh lo, suno ! thikanon mein Namaz padho, phir kaha : jab safar mein raat sard ya barish wali hoti to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) muazzan ko ye kehney ka hukm detey ( أَلَا صَلُّوا فِي الرِّحَالِکُم ( suno ! apni qiyam-gaahon mein Namaz padh lo."
1602,"abu-Usama ne kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne Naafe se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne (Makka se chh mail ke faasley par waaqe ( ) بضَجنانَ ( pahaad par azan kahi . phir uper wali hadis ki tarah bayan kya aur) abu-Usama ne) kaha : ( أَلَا صَلُّوا فِي الرِّحَالِکُم (aur unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke dobara ( أَلَا صَلُّوا فِي الرِّحَالِ ( kehney ka zikr nahi kya."
1603,"Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha : aik safar mein ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikley to barish ho gaee, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, tum mein se jo chahey apni qiyam gaah mein Namaz padh ley."
1604,"Ismail (ibne-Ulaih) ne (ibne-abi Sufiyan) az-Ziyadi ke sathi abdul-hameed se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Haaris se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne aik barish waley din apne muazzan se farmaya : jab tum (  اشهد ان لا اله الا الله اشهد ان محمد ا رسول الله) keh chuko to ( حيي علي الصلوة) na kehna ( balke) ( صَلُّوا فِي بُيُوتِكُمْ ( (apne gharon mein Namaz padho ( kehna . kaha : logon ne maano usko aik ghair Maruf kaam samjha to Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : kya tum is par tajjub kar rahe ho? ye kaam unhon-ne kya jo mujh se bahut zyada behtar they. Juma padhna lazim hai aur mujhey bura malum hua ke main tumhen tangi mein mubtala karun aur tum keechad phislan mein chal kar aao."
1605,"abu-Kamil Jahdari ne kaha : hamein Hammad , yani ibne-zaid ne abdul-hameed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Abdullah-bin-Haaris se suna, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik phislan waley din hamarey samney khutba diya. aagey ibne-Ulaih ki hadis ke ham mana riwayat bayan ki, lekin Jumey ka naam nahi liya, aur kaha : ye kaam us shakhsiyat ne kya hai jo mujh se bahut zyada behtar they, yani Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (ye kaam kya hai) abu-Kamil ne kaha : Hammad ne ham se ye hadis ( abdul-hameed ki bajaey) Aasim se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Haaris se isi tarah riwayat ki hai."
1606,"abu Rabe Atki Zahrani ne kaha : hamein Hammad yani ibne-zaid ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Ayub aur Aasim ahwal ne is sanad ke sath hadis sunai, albatta unhon ( abu Rabe ( ne apni hadis mein (yani Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ke alfaz zikr nahi kiye."
1607,"Shoba ne kaha : hamein abdul-Hameed sahib Ziyadi ne hadis sunai, kaha : maine Abdullah-bin-Haaris se suna, unhon-ne kaha, Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke muazzan ne Jumey ke roz barish waley din azan di. padhi. phir ibne-Ulaih ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya, aur kaha : maine is baat ko na-pasand kya ke tum phislan mein chal kar aao ."
1608,"Shoba aur Mamar donon ne (apni apni sanad se riwayat kartey huey) Aasim ahwal se aur unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Haaris se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne muazzan ko hukm diya. Mamar ki riwayat mein hai : Jumey ke roz barish ke din .) aagey ( pichhli rawiyon ki riwayat ki tarah hai. aur Mamar ki hadis mein ye bhi hai : ye kaam unhon-ne kya jo mujh se bahut zyada behtar hain, yani Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne."
1609,Wuhaib ne kaha : hamein Ayub ne Abdullah-bin-Haaris se hadis bayan ki. Wuhaib ne kaha : Ayub ne ye hadis Abdullah-bin-Haaris se nahi suni. ( jabke ibne- hijr (Raziallahu anhu) ki tehqiq hai ke Wuhaib ki baat durust nahi balke Ayub ne ye hadis suni hai) unhon-ne kaha : Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Jumey ke roz barish ke din apne muazzan ko hukm diya. ( aagey isi tarah hai) jis tarah doosrey rawiyon ne bayan kya.
1610,"Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bin Numer ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein mere walid ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne Naafe se unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (safar mein sawari par) apni nafl Namaz padhtey they aap ki ontni jis taraf bhi aapko liye huey rukh kar leti ."
1611,abu-Khalid Ahmar ne Ubaidullah se unhon-ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni sawari par Namaz padhtey they. wo chahey aapko liye huey jis taraf bhi rukh kar leti .
1612,"Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Abdul-Malik bin abi Sulaiman se riwayat ki, kaha : hamein Saeed-bin-Jubair ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Makka se Madina ki taraf aa rahe hotey , apni sawari par Namaz padhtey they, jis taraf bhi aap ka rukh ho jata. kaha : usi ke barey mein ye aayat utri : so jis taraf tum rukh karo, wahin Allah ka chehra hai."
1613,"ibne-Mubarak, ibne-abi-Zayda aur ibne-Numair ne apne walid ke hawale se, sab ne Abdul-Malik se isi sanad ke sath ye hadis riwayat ki aur unmein se ibne-Mubarak aur ibne-abi-Zayda ki riwayat mein hai ke phir Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aayat tilawat ki ( فَأَيْنَمَا تُوَلُّوا فَثَمَّ وَجْهُ اللہ) tum jis taraf bhi rukh karo wahin Allah ka chehra hai aur kaha : ye usi ke barey mein utri hai."
1614,"Amr-bin-Yahyaa Mazni ne Saeed bin Yasar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko gadhey par Namaz padhtey dekha jabke aap ne khaibar ka rukh kya hua tha."
1615,"Abu-Bakar bin Umar-bin Abdur-Rehman bin-Abdullah-bin umr bin-Khattab ne Saeed bin Yasar se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : main Makka ke rastey mein Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath safar kar raha tha. phir jab mujhey subah ho janey ka andesha hua to main sawari se utra aur witr padhey, phir main unse ja mila to Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se puchha : tum kahan ( reh gaey ( they? maine unse kaha : mujhey fajr ho janey ka andesha hua, isliye maine utar kar witr padhey . to Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : kya tumharey liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke amal mein namoona nahi hai? maine kaha : kyon nahi, Allah ki qism hai unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) oont par witr padhtey they."
1616,Imam Malik (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne Abdullah-bin-Dinar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni sawari par Namaz padhtey they wo aapko liye huey jidhar ka bhi rukh kar leti . Abdullah-bin-Dinar ne kaha : Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi yahi kartey they.
1617,ibne-Had ne Abdullah-bin-Dinar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni sawari par witr ada kartey they.
1618,"Salim bin-Abdullah ne apne walid ( Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni sawari par nafl padhtey jidhar bhi aap ka rukh ho jata aur usi par witr bhi padhtey , albatta aap farz Namaz is par nahi padhtey they."
1619,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Aamir-bin-Rabee ne khabar di ke unhein unke walid ne bataya ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, aap safar mein raat ke waqt sawari par nafl padhtey they jidhar ka bhi wo rukh kar leti thi."
1620,"Hammam ne kaha : hamein Anas bin Sirin ne hadis bayan ki ke jab Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) Sham (Syria) se aaey to ham ne unka istiqbaal kya, ham (Ainit-tamr) ke maqam par ja kar unse miley to maine unhein dekha, wo gadhey par Namaz padh rahe they aur unka rukh us taraf tha. Hammam ne qibley ki baain taraf ishara kya. to main ( Anas bin Sirin ( ne unse kaha : maine aapko qibley ki baain taraf Namaz padhtey dekha hai unhon-ne kaha : agar maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aisa kartey huey na dekha hota to main (kabhii) aisa na karta."
1621,Imam Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jab chalney ki jaldi hoti to maghrib aur isha ki namazein jama kar letey.
1622,Ubaidullah se riwayat hai kaha : mujhey Naafe ne khabar di ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko jab (safar ke liye) jaldi chalnaa hota to shafaq ( suraj ki surkhi ( ghayab honey ke baad (yani isha ka waqt shuru honey ke baad) maghrib aur isha ko jama karke padhtey they aur bataatey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jab jald chalna hota to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maghrib aur isha ko jama kar letey they.
1623,"Sufiyan ne (ibne-Shahab) Zohri se, unhon-ne Salim se aur unhon-ne apne walid ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, jab aapko chalney ki jaldi hoti to aap maghrib aur isha ko jama kar letey they."
1624,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Saalim-bin-Abdullah ne khabar di ke unke walid ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha jab aap ne safar mein jald chalna hota to maghrib ki Namaz ko muakhkhar kar detey yahan tak ke usey aur isha ki Namaz ko jama kartey."
1625,"Mufazzal bin Fazala ne Aqeel se, unhon-ne ibne-Shahab se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab suraj dhalney se pahley kooch kartey to Zohar ko us waqt tak muakhkhar farmatey ke Asr ka waqt ho jata, phir aap ( sawari se) utartey , donon namazon ko jama kartey, aur agar aap ke kooch karne se pahley suraj dhal jata to Zohar padh kar sawar hotey."
1626,"Lais-bin-Sad ne Aqeel-bin-Khalid se baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) safar mein jab 2 namazon ko jama karna chahtey to Zohar ko muakhkhar kartey yahan tak ke Asr ka awwal waqt ho jata, phir aap donon namazon ko jama kartey."
1627,"Jaabir bin Ismail ne bhi Aqeel-bin-Khalid se baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jab safar mein jaldi hoti to Zohar ko Asr ke awwal waqt tak muakhkhar kar detey, phir donon ko jama kar letey aur maghrib ko muakhkhar kartey aur isha ke sath ikattha karke padhtey jab shafaq ghayab ho jati."
1628,"Imam Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zohar aur Asr ko ikattha padha aur maghrib aur isha ko ikattha padha kisi khof aur safar ke baghair ."
1629,"Zuhair ne kaha : hamein abu-Zubair ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zohar aur Asr ko Madina mein kisi khof aur safar ke baghair jama karke padha . abu-Zubair ne kaha : maine (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke shagird ( Saeed se puchha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisa kyon kya tha? unhon-ne jawab diya : maine bhi Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se sawal kya tha jaisey tum ne mujh se sawal kya hai to unhon-ne kaha : aap ne chaha ke apni ummat ke kisi fard ko tangi aur dushwaari mein na daalein ."
1630,"Qurra bin Khalid ne kaha : hamein abu-Zubair ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Saeed-bin-Jubair ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) taala anhumaa ne hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jange-Tabook ke doran aik safar mein namazon ko jama kya, Zohar aur Asr ko ikattha padha aur maghrib aur isha ko ikttha padha . Saeed ne kaha maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisa kyon kya tha? unhon-ne kaha : aap ne chaha apni ummat ko harj (aur tangi) mein na daalein ."
1631,Zuhair ne kaha : hamein abu-Zubair ne abu Tufail Aamir se hadis sunai aur unhon-ne Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke ham jange-Tabook main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikley to (is doran mein) aap Zohar aur Asr ikatthi padhtey rahe aur maghrib aur isha ko jama kartey rahe.
1632,"Qurra bin Khalid ne kaha : hamein abu-Zubair ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Aamir bin Wasila abu Tufail ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hazrat Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jange-Tabook mein Zuhar, Asr ko aur maghrib , isha ko jama kya. ( Aamir bin Wasila ne) kaha : maine (Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se) puchha : aap ne aisa kyon kiya? to unhon-ne kaha : aap ne chaha ke apni ummat ko dushwari mein na daalein ."
1633,"abu-Muawiya aur Wakee donon ne Aamash se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Habib bin Sabit se unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zuhar, Asr aur maghrib , isha ko Madina mein kisi khof aur barish ke baghair jama kya. Wakee ki riwayat mein hai) Saeed ne) kaha : maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisa kyon kiya? unhon-ne kaha : taake apni ummat ko dushwari mein mubtala na karein aur abu-Muawiya ki hadis mein hai Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha gaya : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya chahtey huey aisa kiya? unhon-ne kaha : aap ne chaha apni ummat ko dushwari mein na daalein ."
1634,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Amr-bin-Dinar se unhon-ne ( abu-Shasha ( Jaabir bin Zaid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aath (8) rakaat (zuhar aur Asr ( ikatthi aur saat (7) rakaat ( maghrib aur isha ( ikatthi padhein. ( Amr ne kaha ( maine abu Shasha ( Jaabir bin Zaid ( se kaha ke mera khayal hai aap ne Zohar ko muakhkhar kya aur Asr jaldi padhi aur maghrib ko muakhkhar kya aur isha mein jaldi ki. unhon-ne kaha : mera bhi yahi khayal hai."
1635,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Amr-bin-Dinar se unhon-ne Jaabir bin Zaid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Madina mein saat (7) rakaat aur aath (8) rakaat Namaz padhi. yani Zuhar, Asr, maghrib aur isha ( mila kar padhin)."
1636,"Zuber bin Khirrit ne Abdullah-bin Shaqiq se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : aik din Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) Asr ke baad hamein Khitab karne lagey yahan tak ke suraj ghurub ho gaya aur sitaarey namudaar ho gaey aur log kehney lagey : Namaz , Namaz ! phir unke paas banu- Tameem ka aik aadmi aaya jo na thaktaa tha aur na baaz aa raha tha Namaz , Namaz kahey ja raha tha, Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha teri maan na ho ! to mujhey sunnat sikhaa raha hai? phir kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha aap ne Zohar w Asr ko aur maghrib w ishaa ko jama kya. Abdullah-bin Shaqiq ne kaha : to us se mere dil mein kuchh khatakney laga, chunanche main Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur unse puchha to unhon-ne un (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) ke qaul ki tasdeeq ki."
1637,"Imran bin Hudair ne Abdullah-bin Shaqiq Aqili se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik shakhs ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : Namaz ! aap khamosh rahe us ne phir kaha : Namaz ! aap phir chup rahe, us ne phir kaha : Namaz ! to aap ( kuchh der ( chup rahe, phir farmaya : teri maan na ho ! kya to hamein Namaz ki taleem deta hai? ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daur mein 2 namazein jama kar liya kartey they."
1638,"abu-Muawiya aur Wakee ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Umara se, unhon-ne Aswad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) (bin Masood ( se riwayat ki, kaha : tum mein se koi shakhs apni zaat mein se shaitan ka hissa na rakhey (waham aur waswasey ka shikar na ho ( ye khayal na karey ke is par lazim hai ke wo Namaz se daain ke ilawa kisi aur taraf se rukh na modey , maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aksar dekha tha, aap baain taraf se rukh Mubarak modtey they."
1639,Jarir Esa-bin-Yonus ne isi sanad ke sath pichhli hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
1640,"abu-Awana ne (Ismail bin Abdur-Rehman ( Suddi se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : jab main Namaz padh loon to apna rukh kaisey modun, apni daain taraf ya apni baain taraf se ? unhon-ne kaha : maine to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko zyada tar daain taraf se rukh phertey dekha hai."
1641,Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Suddi se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni daain taraf se rukh phera akrtey they.
1642,"ibne-abi-Zayda ne Misar se, unhon-ne Sabit bin Ubaid se unhon-ne Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ke betey ( Ubaid ( se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha ke jab ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey Namaz padhtey to pasand kartey they ke ham aap ki daain taraf hon, aap hamari taraf rukh farmaein .) Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : maine ( aisey hi aik mauqe par) aapko ye farmatey huey suna : aey mere rab! to jab apne bandon ko uthaaeyga ya jama karega us din mujhey apne azab se bachaana."
1643,Wakee ne Misar se isi sanad ke sath ye hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne ( يُقْبِلُ عَلَيْنَا بِوَجْهِهِ ( (aap hamari taraf rukh farmaaein) ke alfaz zikr nahi kiye.
1644,"Shoba ne Warqa se unhon-ne Amr-bin-Dinar se, unhon-ne Ata-bin-Yasar se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jab Namaz ke liye iqamat ho jaey to farz Namaz ke siwa koi Namaz nahi."
1645,(Shoba ki bajaey) Shababaa ne Warqa se yahi riwayat isi sanad ke sath bayan ki hai.
1646,"Rooh ne kaha : hamein Zakariya-bin Ishaq ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha, hamein Amr-bin-Dinar ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Ata-bin-Yasar se suna wo keh rahe they : Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : jab Namaz ke liye iqamat kahi jaey to farz Namaz ke siwa koi Namaz nahi hoti ."
1647,(Rooh ki bajaey) Abdur-Razzaq ne khabar di ke hamein Zakariya-bin Ishaq ne isi sanad ke sath isi tarah khabar di.
1648,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Ayub se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Amr-bin-Dinar se unhon-ne Ata-bin-Yasar se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se pichhli hadis ki manind (tarah) riwayat ki. Hammad ne kaha : phir main (seedhey-seedhey) Amr (bin Dinar) se mila to unhon-ne mujhey ye hadis sunai lekin unhon-ne us hadis ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf mansub nahi kya. ( Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ka qaul riwayat kya ("
1649,"Abdullaah-bin-Muslima Qanabi ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha hamein Ibrahim bin Sad ne apne walid se hadis sunai. unhon-ne Hafs bin Aasim se aur unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Malik ibne- Buhaina (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik shakhs ke paas se guzrey jo Namaz padh raha tha jab subah ki Namaz ke liye iqamat kahi ja chuki thi aap ne kisi cheez ke barey mein us se guftgu farmai ham na jaan sakey ke wo kya thi jab ham Namaz se farigh huey to ham ne usey gher liya ham poochh rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tum se kya kaha? us ne bataya : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : lagta hai ke tum mein se koi subah ki char rakaat padhney lageyga. Qanabi ne kaha : Abdullah-bin Malik ibne- Buhaina (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne walid se riwayat ki. abul-Husain Muslim (Raziallahu anhu) (muallif kitab) ne kaha : Qanabi ka us hadis main ( عَنْ أَبِيهِ ( ) walid se riwayat ki) kehna durust nahi. ( Abdullah ke walid Malik sahabi to hain lekin unse koi hadis marwi nahi)"
1650,"abu-Awana ne Sad bin Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Hafs bin Aasim se, aur unhoney Hazrat ( Abdullah ( ibne- Buhaina (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : subah ki Namaz ki iqamat ( shuru ( hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik shakhs ko Namaz padhtey dekha jabke muazzan iqamat keh raha hai to aap ne farmaya : kya tum subah ki char rakatein padhogey?"
1651,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin Sarjis se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : aik aadmi masjid mein aaya jabke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) subah ki Namaz padha rahe they, us ne masjid ke aik koney mein 2 rakatein padhein, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz mein Sharik ho gaya, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne salam phera to farmaya : aey falan! tu ney 2 namazon mein se kon si Namaz ko shumaar kya hai? apni us Namaz ko jo tum ne akeley padhi hai ya usko jo hamarey sath padhi hai?"
1652,"Yahya-bin-Yahya ne kaha : hamein Salman bin Bilal ne Rabia bin Abdur-Rehman se khabar di, unhon-ne Abdul-Malik bin Saeed se, aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu Humaid (Raziallahu anhu) . ya Hazrat abu Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jab tum mein se koi shakhs masjid mein dakhil ho to kahey ( اللَّهُمَّ افْتَحْ لِي أَبْوَابَ رَحْمَتِكَ (aey Allah ! mere liye apni rehmat ke darwazey khol de. aur jab masjid se nikley to kahey ( اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَسْأَلُكَ مِنْ فَضْلِكَ (aey Allah ! main tujh se terey Fazal ka sawal karta hun. Imam Muslim (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Yahya-bin-Yahya se suna, wo kehtey they, maine ye hadis Sulaiman-bin Bilal ki kitab se likhi hai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey ye khabar pahunchi hai. ke Yahya Himmani shak ke baghair abu Usaid se kehtey they."
1653,"(Sulaiman-bin-Bilal ke bajaey) Umaara-bin-Ghaziya ne Rabee-bin-abi Abdur-Rehman se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Abdul-Malik bin-Saeed-bin-suwed Ansari se. unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Humaid . ... . ya Hazrat abu Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
1654,Aamir-bin-Abdullah-bin Zuber ne Amr-bin-Sulaim-Zarqi se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs masjid mein dakhil ho to baithney se pahley do rakaat Namaz padhey.
1655,"Muhammad-bin-Yahyaa-bin-hibbaan ne Amr-bin-Sulaim-bin-khulda Ansari se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahabi Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : main masjid mein dakhil hua jabke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon ke darmyan tashrif-farma they kaha : to main bhi baith gaya, is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumhen baithney se pahley do rakaat Namaz padhney se kis cheez ne rokaa hai? maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! maine aapko baithtey dekha hai aur log bhi baithey they (is liye main bhi baith gaya) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs masjid mein aaey to do rakaat Namaz padhey baghair na baithey."
1656,"Sufiyan-bin-Maharib-bin-Disaar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mera Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zimmey qarz tha, aap ne usey ada kya aur mujhey zayada raqam di aur jab main aap ki masjid mein dakhil hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : do rakaat Namaz ada kar lo."
1657,"Shoba ne Maharib se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se aik oont khareedaa , jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina pahunchey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey hukm diya ke main masjid mein aaoon , aur do rakatein padhun."
1658,"Wahab-bin-kaisaan ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main aik ghazwey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikla , mere oont ne mujhey der kara di aur thak gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujh se pahley Madina mein aagey aur main agley din pahuncha , main masjid mein aaya to maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko masjid ke darwazey par paya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : tum ab is waqt pahunchey ho? maine kaha : ji haan. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : apna oont chhod do aur masjid mein dakhil ho kar do rakatein padho . main masjid mein dakhil hua, Namaz padhi, par wapas (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ( aaya."
1659,"Hazrat Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) din mein chasht ke waqt ke siwa ( kisi aur waqt) safar se wapas tashrif na latey , phir jab tashrif latey to masjid jatey, usmein do rakatein ada kartey, phir ( kuchh der ( wahin tashrif rakhtey (taake ghar walon ko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aamad ka ilm ho jaey) ."
1660,"Saeed Jurairi ne Abdullah-bin Shaqiq se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha : kya Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chasht ki Namaz padhtey they? unhon-ne kaha : nahi, siwaey-iske ke bahar (safar ( se wapas aaey hun."
1661,"Kahmas bin Hasan Qaisi ne Abdullah-bin Shaqiq se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha : kya Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chasht ki Namaz padha kartey they? unhon-ne jawab diya : nahi siwaey-iske ke safar se wapas aaey hun."
1662,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine kabhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko) ghar mein qiyam ke doran mein) chasht ke nafl padhtey nahi dekha, jabke mein chasht ki Namaz padhti hun. ye baat yaqeeni hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi kaam ko karna pasand farmatey they. lekin us dar se ke log ( bhi aapko dekh kar) wo kaam karengey aur (unki dilchaspi ki bina par) wo kaam un par farz kar diya jaeyga, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us kaam ko chhod detey they."
1663,"Abdul-Waris ne kaha : hamein Yazeed rashk ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha, mujhey Muaza ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se sawal kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chasht ki Namaz kitni ( rakatein ( padhtey they? unhon-ne jawab diya char rakatein aur jis qadr zyada padhna chahtey ( padh letey ( ."
1664,"Shoba ne Yazeed se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur Yazeed ne ( maashaa (ke bajaey) ( mashaAllah ( ) jitni Allah chahta ( kaha,"
1665,"Saeed ne kaha : Qatada ne hamein hadis bayan ki ke Muaza adwiya ne un ( hadis sunney walon ( ko Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chasht ki Namaz char rakatein padhtey they. aur Allah Taala jis qadr chahta zyada ( bhi) padh letey."
1666,"Muaz bin Hisham ne riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey mere walid ne Qatada se isi sanad ke sath yahi hadis bayan ki."
1667,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna aur ibne-Bashar ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Amr-bin-Murra se unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin abi Lela se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Umme-Hani (Raziallahu anhu) ke siwa kisi ne ye nahi bataya ke usne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko chasht ki Namaz padhtey dekha. unhon-ne bataya ke fateh Makka ke din Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke ghar mein tashrif laey aur aap ne aath (8) rakatein padhein , maine aapko kabhi us se halki Namaz padhtey nahi dekha, haan aap rukoo aur sujood mukammal tareeqey se kar rahe they. ibne-Bashar ne apni riwayat main ( qat ( (kabhi) ka lafz bayan nahi kya."
1668,"Hurmala bin Yahya aur Muhammad-bin Salma Muradi donon ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Abdullah-bin Wahab ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se khabar di, kaha : mujhey Abdullah-bin-Haaris ke betey ne hadis sunai ke unke walid Abdullah-bin-Haaris bin Nofal ne kaha : maine (sab se) puchha aur meri ye shadeed khahish thi ke mujhey koi aik shakhs mil jaey jo mujhey bataaey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chasht ki Namaz padhi hai. mujhey Umme-Hani binte-abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ke siwa koi na mila jo mujhey ye bataataa . unhon-ne mujhey khabar di ke fateh Makka ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) din buland honey ke baad tashrif laaey, aik kapda la kar aapko parda muhaiya kya gaya, aap ne ghusl farmaya, phir aap khadey huey aur aath (8) rakatein padhin. main nahi janti ke unmein aap ka qiyam (nisbatan) zyada lamba tha ya aap ka rukoo ya aap ka sujood ye sab ( arkaan ( qareeb qareeb they aur unhon-ne ( Umme-Hani (Raziallahu anhu)) ne bataya , maine us se pahley aur uske baad aapko nahi dekha ke aap ne ye Namaz padhi ho. ( Muhammad-bin-Muslima ( Muradi ne apni riwayat mein Yunus se riwayat hai kaha, mujhey Yunus ne khabar di nahi kaha,"
1669,"abu-Nazar se riwayat hai ke Umme-Hani binte-abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke main fateh Makka ke saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf gaee to maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko nahatey huey paya jabke aap ki beti Fatima (Raziallahu anha) aapko kapdey se chhipaaey huey thin ( aagey parda kya hua tha) maine salam arz kya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ye kon hai? maine kaha : Umme-Hani binte-abi-Talib hun. aap ne farmaya : Umme-Hani ko khush aamadeed ! jab aap nahaaney se farigh huey to khadey huey aur sirf aik kapdey mein liptey huey aath (8) rakatein padhein , jab aap Namaz se farigh ho gaey to maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mera maan-jaya bhai Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) chahta hai ke aik aisey aadmi ko qatl kar de jisey main panah de chuki hun. yani Hubaira ka betaa, falan, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Umme-Hani! jis ko tum ne panah di usey ham ne bhi panah di. Umme-Hani (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ye chasht ka waqt tha."
1670,"Jafar bin-Muhammad (Raziallahu anhu) ke walid Muhammad Baaqar (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne Aqeel ke aazad karda ghulam abu Murra se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Umme-Hani (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke fateh Makka ke saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke ghar mein aik kapdey mein jiske donon kinarey aik doosrey ki mukhalif taraf daley gaey they, aath (8) rakatein padhin."
1671,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : subah ko tum mein se har aik shakhs ke har jod par aik sadqa hota hai. to har aik tasbeeh (eik baar (Subhanallah) kehna ( sadqa hai. har aik tamheed ( الحمد لله ( kehna ( sadqa hai, har aik tahleel ( la ilaa-h illallaah ( kehna ( sadqa hai har aik takbeer ( Allahu-akbar ( kehna ( bhi sadqa hai. ( kisi ko) neki ki talqeen karna sadqa hai aur (kisi ko) burai se roknaa bhi sadqa hai. aur un tamam baaton ki jagah 2 rakatein jo insan chasht ke waqt padhta hai kifaayat karti hain."
1672,"abu Tayyah ne kaha : hamein abu-Usmaan Nehdi ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey mere khaleel (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teen chizon ki talqeen farmai, har maah teen rozey rakhney ki, chasht ki 2 rakaton ki aur is baat ki ke soney se pahley witr padh liya karun."
1673,"Abbas, jariri, aur abu shimr zib-e, donon ne kaha : ham ne abu-Usman Nehdi se suna, wo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kar rahe they aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi pichhli hadis ki manind (tarah) hadis bayan ki."
1674,"abu Raafe Saaigh ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha, mujhey mere khaleel abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teen baton ki talqeen farmai . aagey Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se abu-Usman nehdi ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya."
1675,"Hazrat abu Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : mere Habib (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey teen baton ki talqeen farmai hai, jab tak mein zinda rahunga unko kabhi tark nahi karunga, har maah teen dinon ke rozey , chasht ki Namaz aur ye ke jab tak witr na padh loon na soun."
1676,Imam Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Ummul-Momenin Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein bataya ke jab muazzan subah ki azan keh kar khamosh ho jata aur subah zahir ho jati to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz ki iqamat se pahley 2 mukhtasar rakatein padhtey .
1677,"Lais-bin-Sad, Ubaidullah aur Ayub sab ne Naafe se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah riwayat bayan ki hai jis tarah Imam Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne ki."
1678,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Zaid-bin Muhammad se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Naafe se suna, wo Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kartey they aur wo Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat bayan kar rahe they Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : jab fajr tuloo ho jati to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) 2 mukhtasar rakaton ke siwa koi Namaz na padhtey they."
1679,"(Muhammad-bin-Jafar ki bajaey) nazar ne hamein khabar di, kaha : Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath usi pichhli hadis ki manind (tarah) hadis bayan ki hai."
1680,"Salim ne apne walid (Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne mujhey khabar di ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney jab fajr roshan ho jati to aap 2 rakatein Namaz padhtey they."
1681,"Abda bin Sulaiman ne kaha : hamein Hisham-bin-Urwa ne apne walid ke hawale se Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se hadis bayan ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) azan suntey to fajr ki 2 rakatein padhtey aur unmein kami kartey they."
1682,"Ali-bin-Mus-hir, abu-Usama, Abdullah-bin-Numair, aur Wakee sab ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath yahi hadis riwayat ki, albatta abu-Usama ki riwayat mein (jab azan sunney ki bajaey) jab fajr tuloo hoti ke alfaz hain."
1683,abu-Salma ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) subah ki Namaz ki azan aur iqamat ke darmyan 2 rakatein padhtey they.
1684,Yahya-bin-Saeed ne kaha : mujhey Muhammad-bin Abdur-Rehman ne bataya ke unhon-ne Umra ko Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se hadis bayan kartey huey suna wo kaha karti thin ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) subah ki) sunnat ( 2 rakatein padhtey aur unko itna halka padhtey ke main (dil mein) kehti thi : kya aap ne unmein Fatiha bhi padhi hai ya nahi? (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) umuman Fatiha bhi bahut thahar thahar kar padhtey they. (
1685,"Shoba ne Muhammad-bin Abdur-Rehman Ansari se riwayat ki. unhon-ne Umra binte-Abdur-Rehman se suna, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha jab fajr tuloo ho jati to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) 2 rakatein ada kartey. (dil mein) kehti kya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unmein Fatiha padhtey hain?"
1686,"Yahya-bin-Saeed ne ibne-Juraij se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Ata-bin Ubaid-bin-Umair se hadis sunai aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) nawaafil mein se kisi aur (namaz ( ki itni zyada paasdari nahi kartey they jitni aap subah se pahley ki 2 rakaton ki kartey they."
1687,"Hafs ne ibne-Juraij se baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kisi bhi nafl (ki adaaeygi (ke liye is qadr jaldi kartey nahi dekha jitni jaldi aap namaze-Fajr se pahley ki 2 rakaton ke liye kartey they."
1688,"abu-Awana ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Zarara-bin-Ufa se, unhon-ne Sad bin Hisham se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : fajr ki 2 rakatein duniya aur jo kuchh duniya mein hai, us se behtar hain."
1689,Motamir ke walid Sulaiman-bin-Tarkhan ne Qatada se isi sanad ke sath Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne tuloo fajr ke waqt ki 2 rakaton ke barey mein farmaya : wo 2 (rakatein) mujhey saari duniya se zyada pasand hain.
1690,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fajr ki 2 rakaton main ( قُلْ يَا أَيُّهَا الْكَافِرُ‌ونَ (aur (قُلْ هُوَ اللہ أَحَدٌ) tilawat kin.
1691,"Marwan bin Muawiya fazari ne Usman bin-Hakim Ansari se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Saeed bin Yasar ne bataya ke unhein Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fajr ki 2 rakaton mein se pehli mein) Quran Majeed se aayat ( ) قُولُوا آمَنَّا بِاللَّـهِ وَمَا أُنزِلَ إِلَيْنَا ( ) wala hissey ( padhtey jo sura Baqra ki aayat hai aur dusri main ( aale-Imran ki aayat ( ) آمَنَّا بِاللہ وَاشْهَدْ بِأَنَّا مُسْلِمُونَ ( ) wala hissey ( padhtey ."
1692,"abu-Khalid Ahmar ne Usman bin-Hakim se, unhon-ne Saeed bin Yasar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fajr ki 2 rakaton main ( Quran Majeed mein se) ( قُولُوا آمَنَّا بِاللَّـهِ وَمَا أُنزِلَ إِلَيْنَا ( ) wala hissey (aur jo sura Aale-Imran mein hai) تَعَالَوْا إِلَىٰ كَلِمَةٍ سَوَاءٍ بَيْنَنَا وَبَيْنَكُمْ ( ) wala hissey ( padha kartey they."
1693,Esa-bin-Yonus ne Usman bin-Hakim se isi sanad ke sath Marwan fazari ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
1694,"abu-Khalid Sulaiman-bin-Hayyan ne Daawood-bin-abii-Hind se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Naumaan-bin-Saalim se aur unhon-ne Amr-bin-aos se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey anbasaa-bin-abi-Sufiyan ne apne marzul-maut mein aik aisi hadis sunai jis se intihai khushi hasil hoti hai, kaha : maine Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo kehti thin : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna jisne aik din aur aik raat mein baara rakaat ada kiin uske liye unke badley jannat mein aik ghar bana diya jata hai. Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jab se maine unke barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, maine unhein kabhi tark nahi kya. anbasaa ne kaha : jab se maine unke barey mein Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, maine unhein kabhi tark nahi kya. Amr-bin-aos ne kaha : jab se maine unke barey mein anbasaa se suna, maine unhein kabhi tark nahi kya. Naumaan-bin-Saalim ne kaha : jab se maine Amr-bin-aos se unke barey mein suna, maine unhein kabhi tark nahi kya."
1695,"Bashar-bin-Mufazzal ne kaha : hamein Dawud ne Naumaan-bin-Saalim se isi sanad ke sath ye hadis bayan ki, jisne aik din mein baara rakaat nawaafil padhey uske liye jannat mein ghar banaya jaeyga."
1696,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Naumaan-bin-Saalim se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Amr-bin-aos se unhon-ne anbasaa-bin-abi-Sufiyan se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi mohtarma Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they : ''koii aisa musalman banda nahi jo har roz Allah ke liye faraaiz ke ilawa baara rakaat sunnatein ada karta hai magar Allah uske liye jannat mein aik ghar bana deta hai. ya uske liye jannat mein aik ghar bana diya jata hai. Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main ab tak unhein musalsal ada karti aa rahi hun. Amr ne kaha : main ab tak unko hamesha ada karta aa raha hun. Nauman ne bhi iske mutabiq kaha.''"
1697,"Behaz ne Shoba se baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis bhi musalman bandey ne ehtimaam ke sath mukammal wuzu kya, phir Allah ki raza ki khaatir har roz ( nafl ( Namaz padhi. padhi. aur usi ke mutabiq riwayat ki."
1698,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Zohar se pahley do rakatein padhein aur uske baad do rakatein aur maghrib ke baad do rakatein aur isha ke baad do rakatein aur Jumey ke baad do rakatein ada ki. jahan tak maghrib , isha aur Jumey (ki sunnaton (ka talluq hai, wo maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aap ke ghar mein padhein."
1699,"Khalid ne Abdullah-bin-Shaqeeq se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha, maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nafl Namaz ke barey mein sawal kiya? to unhon-ne jawab diya : aap mere ghar mein Zohar se pahley char rakaat padhtey , phir (ghar se) nikaltey aur logon ko Namaz padhatey , phir ghar wapas aatey aur do rakatein ada farmatey aur aap logon ko maghrib ki Namaz padhatey phir ghar aatey aur do rakaat Namaz padhtey , aur logon ko isha ki Namaz padhatey aur mere ghar aatey aur do rakatein padhtey , aur raat ko nau (9) rakatein padhtey unmein witr shamil hotey , aur der raat khadey ho kar aur der raat baith kar Namaz ada kartey aur jab khadey ho kar qirat kartey to rukoo aur sajda bhi khadey ho kar kartey aur jab baith kar qirat kartey to rukoo aur sajda bhi baith kar kartey aur jab fajr tuloo (nikalne ko) hoti to do rakatein padhtey."
1700,"Hammad ne Budail aur Ayub se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Shaqiq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ko lamba waqt Namaz padhtey rahtey , to jab aap khadey ho kar Namaz padhtey to khadey khadey rukoo kartey aur jab baith kar Namaz padhtey to baithey huey rukoo kartey."
1701,"Shoba ne Budail se hadis sunai unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Shaqiq se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Faaris (Iraan) mein bimar tha, isliye baith kar Namaz padhta tha. maine iske barey mein Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha to unhon-ne jawab diya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ko lamba waqt khadey ho kar Namaz padhtey they. iske baad (usi tarah) hadis bayan ki."
1702,"Humaid ne Abdullah-bin Shaqiq se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki raat ki Namaz ke barey mein sawal kya to unhon-ne jawab diya : aap raat ko lambe waqt khadey ho kar Namaz padhtey aur raat ko lambe waqt baith kar Namaz padhtey aur jab aap khadey ho kar qirat kartey to khadey khadey rukoo kartey aur jab baith kar qirat kartey to baithey baithey rukoo kartey."
1703,"Muhammad-bin Sirin ne Abdullah-bin Shaqiq Aqili se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham logon ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne kaha aap kasarat se khadey hokar aur baith kar Namaz padhtey they. jab aap khadey ho kar Namaz ki shuruat farmatey to khadey-khadey rukoo kartey aur jab aap baithey huey Namaz ka shuruat kartey to baithey huey rukoo kartey."
1704,"Hisham-bin-Urwa se riwayat hai, kaha : mujhey mere walid ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko nahi dekha tha ke aap ne raat ki Namaz ke kisi hissey mein baith kar qirat ki ho yahan tak ke jab aap ki umr zyada ho gaee to aap baith kar qirat kartey aur jab sura ki tees ya chalis (40) aayatein reh jatin to khadey ho kar unhein padhtey phir rukoo kartey."
1705,"abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baith kar) bhi) Namaz padhtey they, aap baithey huey qirat farmatey jab aap ki qirat se itna hissey bach jata jitni tees ya chalis (40) aayatein hoti hain to aap khadey ho jatey aur khadey huey unki qirat farmatey phir rukoo kartey phir sajda kartey, phir dusri rakaat mein aisa hi kartey."
1706,"Umra ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baithey huey qirat farmatey, to jab rukoo karna chahtey to itni der ke liye khadey ho jatey jitni der mein aik insan chalis (40) aayatein padh leta hai."
1707,"Alqama bin Waqas se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baith kar do rakatein padhtey to kya kartey they? unhon-ne jawab diya : aap unmein qirat kartey rahtey , jab rukoo karne ka irada kartey to khadey ho jatey phir rukoo kartey."
1708,"Saeed bin Jurairi ne Abdullah-bin Shaqiq se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se kaha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baith kar Namaz padh letey they? unhon-ne kaha : haan, jab logon (ke maamlaat ki dekh bhaal aur fikr mandi) ne aapko boodha kar diya."
1709,"Kahmas ne Abdullah-bin Shaqiq se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se kaha, padhi. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah riwayat bayan ki."
1710,abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne khabar di ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka intiqal nahi hua yahan tak ke aap ki Namaz ka bahut sa hissey baithey huey hota tha.
1711,Abdullah-bin Urwa ke walid Urwa-bin-Zubair ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka badan zara badh gaya aur aap bhari ho gaey to aap ki Namaz ka zyada tar hissey baithey huey ( ada ( hota tha.
1712,"Imam Malik ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Saaib bin Yazeed se, unhon-ne Muttalib bin abi Wadaa Sehmi se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko nafl Namaz baith kar kabhi na padhtey dekha tha yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat se aik saal pahley ka zamana hua to aap nafl Namaz baith kar padhney lagey. aap sura ki qirat kartey to usey thahar thahar kar padhtey yahan tak ke wo lambi tareen sura se bhi lambi ho jati. (yani baith kar lekin aur bhi zyada lambi Namaz padhtey )"
1713,"Yunus aur Mamar donon ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath iske jaisi riwayat ki, albatta un donon ( Yunus aur Mamar ( ne aik ya 2 saal kaha."
1714,Hazrat Jaabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat na hui yahan tak ke aap (raat ko) baith kar Namaz padhney lagey.
1715,"Jarir ne mujhey hadis sunai, unhon-ne Mansoor se, unhon-ne Hilaal-bin-Yasaaf se, unhon-ne abu-Yahya se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (bin Aas ( (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey bataya gaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : baith kar aadmi ki Namaz ( ajr mein) aadhi Namaz hai. unhon-ne kaha : aik baar mein aap ke paas aaya aur maine aapko baith kar Namaz padhtey huey paya to maine apna hath aap ke sar Mubarak par lagaya . aap ne puchha : aey Abdullah-bin-Amr tumhen kya hua? maine arz ki, aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey bataya gaya ke aap ne farmaya hai baith kar aadmi ki Namaz aadhi Namaz ke barabar hai. jabke aap baith kar Namaz padh rahe hain. aap ne farmaya : haan aisa hi hai lekin main tum mein se kisi aik ki tarah nahi hun."
1716,"Shoba aur Sufiyan donon ne Mansoor se usi pichhli sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, albatta Shoba ki riwayat mein hai : abu-Yahya al-Araj se riwayat hai) unhon-ne abu-Yahya ke sath unke laqab al-Araj ka bhi zikr kya hai)"
1717,"Malik ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Urwa se, aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ko giyaara rakaat padhtey they, unmein se aik ke zariey witr ada farmatey, jab aap us (eik rakaat ( se farigh ho jatey to aap apne daain pahlu ke bal let jatey yahan tak ke aap ke paas muazzan aa jata to aap 2 ( nisbatan) halki rakatein padhtey."
1718,"Amr-bin-Haris ne ibne-Shahab se isi sanad ke sath Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) isha ki Namaz se jis ko log utma kehtey hain faraghat ke baad se fajr tak gyara (11) rakaat padhtey they. har 2 rakaat par salam phertey aur witr aik rakaat padhtey . jab muazzan subah ki Namaz ki azan keh kar khamosh ho jata aap ke samney subah waazeh ho jati aur muazzan aap ke paas aa jata to aap uth kar do halki rakatein padhtey phir apne daahiney pahlu ke bal let jatey yahan tak ke muazzan aap ke paas iqamat (ki itlaa deney) ke liye aa jata."
1719,"Hurmala ne mujhey ye hadis bayan ki (kaha ( hamein ibne- Wahab ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha, mujhey Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se isi sanad ke sath khabar di. aagey Hurmala ne pichhli hadis ki manind (tarah) hadis bayan ki albatta usmein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney subah ke roshan ho janey aur muazzan aap ke paas aata ke alfaz zikr nahi kiye aur iqamat ka zikr kya. baqi hadis bilkul Amr ki hadis ki tarah hai."
1720,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne hamein hadis bayan ki aur kaha : hamein Hisham ne apne walid ( Urwa ( se hadis sunai aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ko 13 rakatein padhtey they, unmein se panch rakaton ke zariey witr ( ada ( kartey they, unmein aakhiri rakat ke ilawa kisi mein bhi tashahud ke liye na baithtey they. ( kuchh raaton mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye mamool (routine) hota ("
1721,"Abda bin Sulaiman , Wakee aur abu-Usama sab ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath (ye ( riwayat bayan ki hai."
1722,Urwa bin Malik ne Urwa se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fajr ki 2 rakaton samet 13 rakatein padha kartey they.
1723,"Saeed-bin-abi-Saeed Maqbari ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha : Ramazan mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz kaisey hoti thi? unhon-ne jawab diya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ramazan aur uske ilawa (doosrey mahinon ( mein) fajr se pahley) gyara (11) rakaton se zayed nahi padhtey they, char rakatein padhtey , unki khoobsoortii aur unki tawaalat ke barey mein mat poochho , phir char rakatein padhtey , unke Hasan aur tawaalat ke barey mein na poochho , phir teen rakatein padhtey . Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! kya aap witr padhney se pahley so jatey hain? to aap ne farmaya : aey Aaisha ! meri aankhen soti hain aur mera dil nahi sota . (wo badastoor Allah ke zikr mein mashghool rehtaa hai.)"
1724,"Hisham ne Yahya se aur unhon-ne abu-Salma se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke barey mein sawal kya to unhon-ne kaha aap terah (13) rakatein padhtey they, aath (8) rakatein padhtey phir (eik rakaat se) witr ada farmatey, phir baithey huey do rakatein padhtey , phir jab rukoo karna chahtey to uth khadey hotey aur rukoo kartey, phir subah ki Namaz ki azan aur iqamat ke darmyan do rakatein padhtey. (kabhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki tahajjud aur witr ki tarteeb ye bin jati thi.)"
1725,"Sheban aur Muawiya-bin-Salam ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey abu-Salma ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz ke barey mein poochha. padhi. aagey pichhli hadis ki tarah hai, albatta un donon ki riwayat mein hai : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey ho kar nau (9) rakatein padhtey they witr unhi mein ada kartey."
1726,"Abdullah-bin-abii-labeed se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne abu-Salma se suna, unhon-ne kaha : main Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha : aey meri maan ! mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz ke barey mein bataiye . to unhon-ne kaha : Ramazan aur ghair Ramazan mein raat ke waqt aap ki Namaz terah (13) rakatein thi, unmein fajr ki) sunnat ( do rakatein bhi shamil thin."
1727,"Qasim-bin-Muhammad se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se suna, farma rahi thin : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki raat ki Namaz das rakatein thi aur aap aik rakaat witr ada kartey, phir fajr ki (sunnatein) do rakaat padhtey. is tarah ye teraah(13) rakatein huin."
1728,"abu-khaisma ( Zuhair-bin-Muawiya ( ne Abu-Ishaq se khabar di, kaha : maine Aswad-bin-Yazeed se us hadis ke barey mein puchha jo unse Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz ke barey mein bayan ki thi. unhon ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ke pahley hissey mein so jatey aur aakhiri hissey ko zinda kartey ( Allah ke samney qiyam farmatey huey jaagtey ( phir agar apne ghar walon se koi zarurat hoti to apni zarurat poori kartey aur so jatey, phir jab pehli azan ka waqt hota to Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : aap uchhal kar khadey ho jatey (rawi ne kaha :) Allah ki qism ! Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne sirf  ''khadey ho jatey''  nahi kaha, ''balki tezi ke saath khadey ho jaatey'' kaha, phir apne uper pani bahaatey , Allah ki qism ! unhon-ne  ''nahatey they'' nahi kaha : ''apne uper pani bahaatey they'' kaha, main janta hun unki murad kya thi? (yani zyada miqdar mein pani bahaatey (aur agar aap junbi (hambistari k baad ki napaki ki haalat me) na hotey to jis tarah aadmi Namaz ke liye wuzu karta hai, isi tarah wuzu farmatey, phir do rakatein (sunnatte-fajr ( ada farmatey."
1729,"Ammar-bin-zuraiq ne Abu-Ishaq se, unhon-ne Aswad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ko Namaz padhtey yahan tak ke unki Namaz ka aakhiri hissey witr hota. (aksar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka mamool (routine) yahi tha.)"
1730,Masruq ne kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke amal ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne kaha : aapko hamesha kiya janey wala amal pasand tha. maine kaha : aap kis waqt Namaz padhtey they? to unhon-ne kaha : jab aap murgh ki awaz suntey to khadey ho jatey aur Namaz padhtey.
1731,"abu-Salma ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : sahar ke aakhiri hissey (jab tuloo fajr se bilkul pahley sahar apni intihaa par hoti hai) ne mere ghar mein ya mere paas , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko soey huey hi paya."
1732,"abu-Nazar ne abu-Salma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab fajr ki sunnatein padh letey to agar main jaagtii hoti mere sath guftgu farmatey, warna let jatey."
1733,"ibne-abi-attaab ne abu-Salma se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
1734,"Urwa-bin-Zubair ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ko Namaz padhtey rahtey , jab witr padhney lagtey to farmatey : Aaisha ! utho aur witr padh lo."
1735,"Qasim-bin-Muhammad ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ko apni Namaz padhtey aur wo ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) (aap ke samney leti hoti thin, jab aap ke witr baqi reh jatey to aap unhein jaga detey aur wo witr padh letin."
1736,"Muslim (bin-sabeeh) ne Masruq-se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne raat ke har hissey mein witr (ya raat ( ki Namaz padhi, ( lekin umuman (aap ke witr sehrii ke waqt tak pahunchtey they."
1737,"Yahya bin wassab  ne Masruq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne raat ke har hissey mein witr (raat ( ki Namaz padhi, raat ke shuruati hissey mein bhi, darmyan mein bhi aur aakhir mein bhi, aap ke witr (ke oqaat ( sehrii tak jatey they."
1738,"abu-zuhaa ne Masruq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne raat ke har hissey mein witr padhey hain, ( lekin umuman (aap ke witr raat ke aakhiri hissey tak chaltey."
1739,"ibne-abi-Adi ne Saeed ( ibne-abi-Aruba ( se, unhon-ne Qatada se aur unhon-ne Zarara se riwayat ki ke) Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke qaribi azeez ( Sad-bin-Hisham-bin-Aamir ne irada kya ke Allah Taala ki raah mein jang (jihad ( karein, wo Madina Munawra aagey aur wahan apni aik jaaidaad farokht karni chahi taake us se hathiyar aur ghodey muhaiya karein aur maut aaney tak roomiyon ke khilaf jihad karein, chunanche jab Madina aaey to ahale-Madina mein se kuchh logon se miley, unhon-ne unko is iraadey se rokaa aur unko bataya ke chh (6) afraad ke aik giroh ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hayaat mubaraka mein aisa karne ka irada kya tha to Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein rok diya tha. aap ne farmaya tha : kya mere tarze-amal main tumharey liye namoona nahi hain? chunanche jab un logon ne unhein ye baat batai to unhon-ne apni biwi se rujoo kar liya jabke wo usey talaaq de chukey they, aur us se rujoo ke liye gawah banaey . phir Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar unse Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke witr (raat ki ibaadet) ke barey mein sawal kya to Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : kya main tumhen us hasti se aagah na karun. jo poori zamin ke tamam logon ki nisbat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke witr ko zyada jaanney wali hai? Sad ne kaha : wo kon hain? unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) unke paas jao aur poochho , phir (dobara) mere paas aana aur unka jawab mujhey bhi aa kar batana , ( Sad ne kaha : ( mein unki taraf chal padaa aur (pahley ( hakeem-bin-aflah ke paas aaya aur unhein apne sath Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas chalney ko kaha to unhon-ne kaha : main unke paas nahi jaaunga kyonke maine unhein ( aapas mein ladney wali) un do jamaton ke barey mein kuchh bhi kehney se rokaa tha. to wo un donon ke barey mein usi tareeqey par chaltey rehney ke siwa aur kuchh na maaniin .) Sad ne) kaha : to maine unhein qism di to wo aa gaey, to ham Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf chal padey , aur unse haziri ki ijazat talab ki, unhon-ne ijazat marahmat farma di aur ham unke ghar ( darwazey ( mein dakhil huey, unhon-ne kaha : kya hakeem ho? unhon-ne usey pehchan liya, usne kaha : ji haan. to unhon-ne kaha : tumharey sath kon hai? usne kaha : Sad-bin-Hisham . unhon-ne puchha : Hisham kon ? usne kaha : Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) (bin-Umayya Ansari (ke betey . to unhon-ne unke liye rehmat ki dua ki aur kalimaat khair kahey . Qatada ne kaha : wo ( Aamir (Raziallahu anhu)) Uhud ki jang mein Shahid ho gaey they. maine kaha : Ummul-Momenin ! mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke khalq Mubarak ke barey mein bataiye . unhon-ne kaha : kya tum Quran nahi padhtey ? maine kaha : kyon nahi ! unhon-ne kaha : Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka akhlaq Quran hi tha (aap ki seerat w kirdaar Quran ka amali namoona thi) kaha : is par maine ye chaha ke uth ( kar chala ( jaun aur maut tak kisi se kuchh na poochhoon , phir achcha zahan mein aaya to maine kaha mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke) raat ke) qiyam ke barey mein bataaein, to unhon-ne kaha : kya tum ( يَا أَيُّهَا الْمُزَّمِّلُ ( nahi padhtey? maine kaha kyon nahi ! unhon-ne kaha : Allah Taala ne is sura ke shuruat mein raat ka qiyam farz qarar diya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke sathiyon ne saal bhar qiyam kya aur Allah Taala ne is sura ki aakhiri aayatein baara maah tak aasman par rokey rakhein yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne is sura ke aakhir mein kami (kamii) ka hukm nazil farmaya to raat ka qiyam farz honey ke baad nafl (main tabdeel (ho gaya. Sad ne kaha : maine kaha : aey Ummul-Momenin ! mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke witr ke barey mein bataiye . to unhon-ne kaha : ham Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye aap ki miswak aur aap ke wuzu ka pani taiyaar karke rakhtey they Allah Taala raat ko jab chahta , aapko bedaar kar deta to aap miswak kartey, wuzu kartey aur phir nau (9) rakatein padhtey , unmein aap aathwein ke ilawa kisi rakaat mein na baithtey , phir Allah ka zikr kartey, uski hamd bayan kartey aur dua farmatey, phir salam pherey baghair khadey ho jatey, phir khadey hokar nawein rakaat padhtey , phir baithtey Allah ka zikr aur hamd kartey aur us se dua kartey, phir salam phertey jo hamein sunatey phir salam ke baad baith kar do rakatein padhtey , to mere betey ! ye gyara (11) rakatein ho gain. phir jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki umr Mubarak badhii aur) jism par kisi had tak) gosht chadh gaya (jism Mubarak bhari ho gaya) to aap saat (7) witr padhney lag gaey aur do rakaton mein wahi kartey jo pahley kartey they ( baith kar padhtey ( to betaa ! ye nau (9) rakatein ho gain aur Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab koi Namaz padhtey to aap pasand kartey ke is par qaaim rahen aur jab neend ya bimari ghalib aa jati aur raat ka qiyam na kar saktey to aap din ko baara rakatein padh letey. mein nahi janti ke Allah ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi pura Quran aik raat mein padha ho aur na hi aap ne kisi raat subah tak Namaz padhi aur na Ramazan ke siwa kabhi poorey mahiney ke rozey rakhey .) Sad ne) kaha : phir main Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf gaya aur unhein un (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( ki hadis sunai to unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne sach kaha. agar main unke qareeb hota ya unke ghar jata hota to unke paas jata taake wo mujhey ye hadis roo-baroo sunaatiin. (Sad ne) kaha : maine kaha : agar mujhey ilm hota hai ke aap unke yahaan hazir nahi hotey to main aapko unki hadis na sunata. (ye Sad bil-aakhir sarzameene-Hind mein Shahid huey.)"
1740,"Muaz-bin-Hisham ne Qatada se unhon-ne ziraah-bin-oofaa se aur unhon-ne Sad-bin-Hisham se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne biwi ko talaaq de di, phir Madina ki taraf rawaana huey taake apni jaaidaad farokht karein. padhi. ( aagey usi pichhli hadis ki) tarah bayan kya."
1741,"Muhammad-bin-Bishr ne kaha : hamein Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba ne hadis sunai, kaha : ham se Qatada ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne ziraah-bin-oofaa se aur unhon-ne Sad-bin-Hisham se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : main Hazrat Abdullah Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya aur unse witr ke barey mein sawal kya. padhi. (iske baad) unhon-ne apne poorey qissey samet hadis bayan ki aur is mein kaha : unhon (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( ne kaha : kon Hisham ? maine kaha : Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ke betey . unhon-ne kaha : Aamir bahut achchhey insan they Uhud ke din Shahid huey."
1742,"Mamar ne Qatada se aur unhon-ne ziraah-bin-oofaa se riwayat ki ke Sad-bin-Hisham unke padosi they, unhon-ne unko bataya ke unhon-ne apni biwi ko talaaq de di. padhi. aagey Saeed (bin-abi-arooba (ke ham mana hadis bayan ki. usmein hai, (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : kon Hisham ? kaha : Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ke betey . unhon-ne kaha : wo achchhey insan they Uhud ki jang main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ( ladtey huey) Shahid huey, neez (isii ke saath) is (riwaayat ( mein hai ke (Sad ke bajaey) hakeem-bin-aflah ne kaha : agar main janta ke aap unke paas hazir nahi hotey to main aapko unki hadis na bataataa."
1743,"abu-Awana ne Qatada se, unhon-ne ziraah-bin-oofaa se, unhon-ne Sad-bin-Hisham se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab aap ki raat ki Namaz bimari ya kisi aur wjah se reh jati to din ko baara rakatein padh letey."
1744,"Shoba ne Qatada se isi sanad ke sath Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab koi kaam kartey to usko barqaraar rakhtey aur jab aap raat sotey reh jatey ya bimar ho jatey to aap din ko baara rakatein padh letey. (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko (kabhii) nahi dekha ke aap ne saari raat subah tak Namaz padhi ho aur na (kabhii) aap ne Ramazan ke siwa musalsal mahiney bhar ke rozey rakhey ."
1745,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-abdul-Qaarii se riwayat hai, kaha : maine Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis kisi ka hizb (Quran ka 1/7) hissey jo umuman aik raat mein tahajjud ke doran mein padha jata tha) ya iska kuchh hissey sotey reh janey ki wjah se reh gaya aur us ne usey namaze-Fajr aur namaaze-zuhr ke darmyan padh liya to iske haq mein ye likha jaeyga, jaisey us ne raat hi ko usey padha ."
1746,"Ayub ne Qasim-Shebani se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) ne kuchh logon ko chasht ke waqt Namaz padhtey dekha to kaha : haan ye log achi tarah jantey hain ke Namaz us waqt ke bajaey aik aur waqt mein padhna afzal hai. be-shak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya awwaabeen ( itaat guzaar , tauba karne waley aur Allah Taala ki taraf rujoo karne waley logon ( ki Namaz us waqt hoti hai. jab (garmi se) oont ke doodh chhudaaey janey waley bachchon ke paon jalney lagtey hain."
1747,"Hisham-bin-abi-Abdullah ne kaha : hamein Qasim Shebani ne Hazrat Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ahale-Qubaa ke paas tashrif laaey, wo log (is waqt) Namaz padh rahe they, to aap ne farmaya : awwaabeen ki Namaz oont ke doodh chhudaaey janey waley bachchon ke paon jalney ke waqt (par hoti) hai."
1748,"Naafe aur Abdullah-bin-Dinar ne Hazrat ibney-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se raat ki Namaz ke barey mein sawal kya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : raat ki Namaz do-do rakatein hain, jab tum mein se kisi ko subah honey ka andesha ho to wo aik rakaat padh ley , ye uski padhi hui (tamam) Namaz ko witr (taaq) bana degi."
1749,"Sufiyan ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Salim se aur unhon-ne apne walid ( Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki ke aik aadmi ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se raat ki Namaz ke barey mein sawal kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : do-do rakatein aur jab tumhen subah honey ka andesha ho to aik rakaat witr padh lo."
1750,Amr ne kaha ibne-Shahab ne us se bayan kya ke usey Saalim-bin-Abdullah-bin-Umar aur Humaid-bin-Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf donon ne Abdullah-bin-Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne kaha : aik aadmi khada hua aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! raat ki Namaz kaisey hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : raat ki Namaz do-do rakaat hai aur jab tumhen subah honey ka khatrah ho to aik rakaat (padh kar unhein) witr kar lo.
1751,"abu-Rabe-Zahrani ne kaha : hamein Hammad ne hadis sunai kaha : hamein Ayub aur Budail ne Abdullah-bin-Shaqeeq se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik aadmi ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se poochha, aur main aap ke aur poochhney waley ke darmyan mein tha, usne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! raat ki Namaz kaisey hoti hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : do-do rakatein , phir jab tumhen subah honey ka andesha ho to ek rakaat padh lo aur witr ko apni Namaz ka aakhiri hissey banao . phir saal ke baad aik aadmi ne aap se poochha, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qareeb usi jagah ( darmyan mein) tha aur mujhey malum nahi wo pahley wala aadmi tha ya koi aur , usey bhi aap ne isi tarah jawab diya."
1752,"abu-Kamil ne kaha : hamein Hammad ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Ayub , Budail aur Imran-bin-Hudair ne Abdullah-bin Shaqiq se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, neez (isii ke saath) (doosri sanad se) Muhammad-bin-Ubaid-Ghabari ne kaha : hamein Hammad ne hadis sunai, kaha : ham se Ayub aur Zubair-bin-Khirrit ne Abdullah-bin-Shaqeeq se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke aik aadmi ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sawal kya. padhi. phir donon ( abu-Kamil aur Muhammad-bin-Ubaid ( ne uper wali riwayat bayan ki magar un donon ki riwayat mein aik aadmi ne aap se aik saal guzarney ka baad puchha aur uske baad ka hissa marwi (bayan) nahi."
1753,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : witr padhney mein subah se sabqat karo. (subah honey se pahley-pahley witr padh lo.)
1754,"Leis ne Naafe se riwayat ki ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jo shakhs raat ko Namaz padhey , wo witr ko apni Namaz ka aakhiri hissey banaey kyonke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usi ka hukm detey they."
1755,"Ubaidullah ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : raat ke waqt witr ko apni Namaz ka aakhiri hissey banao ."
1756,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey Naafe ne bataya ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they : jo shakhs raat ko Namaz padhey wo subah se pahley Namaz ka aakhiri hissey witr ko banaey , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un (apne sathiyon ( ko yahi hukm diya kartey they."
1757,"abu-Tayyah ne kaha : mujhey abu-mijliz ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : witr raat ke aakhiri hissey ki aik rakaat hai."
1758,"Shoba ne Qatada se, unhon-ne mijlez se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis bayan kartey they ke aap ne farmaya : witr raat ke aakhiri hissey ki aik rakaat hai."
1759,"Hammam ne kaha : hamein Qatada ne abu-mijlez se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se witr ke barey mein sawal kya to unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they. ( witr (raat ke aakhiri hissey ki aik rakaat hai. aur maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha to unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : ( witr (raat ke aakhir ki aik rakaat hai."
1760,"abu-Kuraib aur Haroon-bin-Abdullah ne kaha : hamein abu-Usama ne Waleed-bin-Kasir se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullah-bin-Umar ne hadis sunai ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke aik aadmi ne jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein they aapko awaz di aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! main raat ki Namaz ko witr ( taaq ( kaisey banaun ? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo (raat ( ki Namaz padhey wo do-do rakaat padhey , phir wo agar mehsus karey ke subah ho rahi hai to aik rakaat padh ley , ye (eik rakaat ( uski saari Namaz ko witr ( taaq ( bana degi. abu-Kuraib ne Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullah kaha, ( aagey ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) nahi kaha."
1761,"Khalaf-bin-Hisham aur abu-Kaamil ne kaha : hamein Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Anas-bin-Sirin se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : subah ki Namaz se pahley ki do rakaton ke barey mein aap ki kya raey hai, kya main unmein lambi qirat kar sakta hoon? unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ko do-do rakaat padhtey they aur aik rakaat se usko witr banatey , maine kaha : main aap se iske barey mein nahi poochh raha. unhon-ne kaha : tum aik bojhal aadmi ho (apni soch ko tarjeeh detey ho) kya mujhey mauqa na doge ke main tumharey liye baat ko mukammal karun? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ko do-do rakaat padhtey they aur aik witr padhtey aur subah (ki Namaz ( se pahley ( mukhtasar si ( do rakatein padhtey , maano ke azan ( iqamat (aap ke kanon mein (sunai de rahi) hai. Khalaf ne apni hadis mein subah se pahley ki do rakaton ke barey mein aap ki raey kya hai? kaha aur unhon-ne Salat (Durud) ka lafz bayan nahi kya."
1762,"Shoba ne Anas-bin-Sirin se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se poochha. phir uper zikr ki gaee hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur is mein ye izafa kya : raat ke aakhiri hissey mein aik rakaat witr padhtey . usmein hai. (aur mere dobara sawal par) kaha : bas, bas, tum aik bojhal aadmi ho."
1763,"Aqba-bin-hurriyat ne kaha : maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo hadis bayan kar rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : raat ki Namaz do rakaat hai aur jab tum dekho ke subah aana chahti hai to aik rakaat se (apni Namaz ko) witr karo. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha gaya : (Musanna, Musanna) ka kya mafhoom hai? unhon-ne kaha : ye ke tum har do rakaton (ke aakhir ( mein salam phero ."
1764,"Mamar ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se, unhon-ne abu-Nazara se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : subah se pahley-pahley witr padh lo."
1765,"Sheban ne Yahya (bin-abi-kaseer ( se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : abu-Nazara-auqii ne mujhey bataya ke Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke unhon (sahaba) ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se witr ke barey mein sawal kiya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : subah honey se pahley witr padh lo."
1766,"Hafs aur abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se hadis sunai, unhon-ne abu Sufiyan se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisey dar ho ke wo raat ke aakhiri hissey mein nahi uth sakega , wo raat ke shuru mein witr padh ley. aur jisey ummeed ho ke wo raat ke aakhir mein uth jaeyga, wo raat ke aakhir mein witr padhey kyonke raat ke aakhiri hissey ki Namaz ka mushaahida (dekha) kiya jata hai aur ye afzal hai. abu-Muawia ne (( mash'hood) ki bajaey) ( mahzoora ( (is mein haziri di jati hai) kaha, (mafhoom aik hi hai)."
1767,"abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : tum mein se jisey ye khadsha (dar) ho ke wo raat ke aakhir mein nahi uth sakega to wo witr padh ley , phir so jaey aur jisey raat ko uth janey ka yaqin ho, wo raat ke aakhir mein witr padhey kyonke raat ke aakhiri hissey mein qirat ke waqt haziri di jati hai. aur ye behtar hai."
1768,"abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyam ka lamba hona behtreen Namaz hai."
1769,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur abu-Kuraib donon ne kaha : hamein abu-Muawiya ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne abu-Sufiyan se hadis sunai aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya : kon si Namaz afzal hai? aap ne farmaya : qiyam ka lamba hona abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : abu-Muawia ne hamein Aamash se hadis bayan ki."
1770,"abu Sufiyan se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : raat mein aik ghadi aisi hai. jo musalman banda bhi usko pa leta hai. usmein wo duniya w aakhirat ki kisi bhi khair aur bhalai ka sawal karta hai to Allah usey wo ( bhalai ( zaroor ata farma deta hai. aur ye ghadi har raat mein hoti hai."
1771,"abu-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : raat mein aik aisi ghadi hai, jo musalman bhi usey pa leta hai aur is mein Allah se kisi bhi khair ka sawal karta hai to wo usey wo ( bhalai ( ata farma deta hai."
1772,"ibne-Shahab ne abu-Abdullah-Agharr aur abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : barkat aur rafa't (bulandi) ka Malik hamara rab , har raat ko jab raat ka aakhiri tehai hissey baqi reh jata hai, (to) duniya ke aa-samaan par nuzool farmata hai aur kehta hai : kon mujhey pukarta hai ke main uski pukar ko sunoon ? kon mujh se mangta hai ke main usko dun, aur kon mujh se bakhshish talab karta hai ke main usey bakhsh dun?"
1773,"Suhel ke walid Abu-Saleh ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : Allah Taala har raat ko , jab raat ka pehlaa tehai hissey guzar jata hai, duniya ke aasman par nuzool farmata hai aur kehta hai : main badshah hoon, sirf main badshah hoon, kon hai jo mujhey pukarta hai hai ke main uski pukar ko sunoon ? kon hai jo mujh se mangta hai ke main usey dun? kon hai jo mujh se maghfirat talab karta hai ke main usey maaf karun? wo yahi elaan farmata rehta hai yahan tak ke subah chamak uthtii hai."
1774,"abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab raat ka aadha ya do tehai hissey guzar jata hai to ek Allah aasmane-duniya par nuzool farmata hai aur kehta hai : kya koi maangney wala hai ke usey diya jaaey? kya koi dua karne wala hai ke uski dua qabool ki jaaey? kya koi bakhshish ka talabgaar hai ke usey bakhshaa jaey yahan tak ke subah phoot padtii hai."
1775,"muhaazir abu- Muwarra' ne kaha : ham se Sad-bin-Saeed (bin-Qais Ansari ( ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey ibne- mar-jaana ne khabar di, unhon ne kaha maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aadhi raat ya raat ki aakhiri tehai ke waqt Allah Taala aasmane-duniya par nuzool farmata hai aur kehta hai : kon mujh se dua karega ke main uski dua qabool karun. ya mujh se sawal karey main usey ata karun? phir farmata hai : kon us ( zaat ( ko qarz dega jo na mohtaaj hai aur na haq maarney wali hai (Allah taala ko)? Imam Muslim ne kaha : ibne- mar-jaana se murad Saeed-bin-Abdullah (abu-usmaan-al-madani)  hain aur mar-jaana unki walida hain."
1776,Sulaiman-bin-Bilal ne Sad-bin-Saeed se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur is mein ye izafa hai : phir Allah Taala apne donon hath phailaataa hai aur farmata hai. : kon usko qarz dega jo na mohtaaj hai aur na hi zaalim.
1777,"Mansoor ne Abu-Ishaq se aur unhon-ne Agharr-abu-Muslim se riwayat ki, wo Hazrat abu-Saeed aur Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain. donon ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala (bandon ko aaraam ki) mohlat deta hai yahan tak ke jab raat ka pahlaa tehai hissey guzar jata hai to wo aasmane-duniya par nuzool farmata hai aur kehta hai : kya koi maghfirat ka talabgar hai? kya koi tauba karne wala hai? kya koi maangney wala hai? kya koi pukarney wala hai? yahan tak ke fajr phoot padtii hai."
1778,"Shoba ne Abu-Ishaq se isi sanad ke sath mazkura (uper zikr) hadis bayan ki, albatta Mansoor ki riwayat mukammal aur zyada (tafseelaat par muheet) hai."
1779,Humaid-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne imaan (ki haalat mein) aur ajr talab kartey huey Ramazan ka qiyam kya uske guzishta tamam gunah maaf kar diye gaey.
1780,"imam Zohri ne abu-Salma (bin-Abdur-Rehman ( se aur unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) lazim thehraaey baghair Ramazan ke qiyam ki targheeb detey they, aap farmatey : jisne Ramazan ka qiyam eman (ki haalat mein) aur ajr talab kartey huey kiya, uske guzishta gunah bakhsh diye jaengey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat tak mamla yahi raha, phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki khilafat aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki khilafat ke shuruati daur mein bhi mamla isi tarah raha (targheeb di jati rahi, ijtimaaii taur par ehtimaam nahi kya gaya)."
1781,"Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ne kaha : hamein Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne hadis bayan ki. ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein hadis sunai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne Ramazan ke rozey eman (ki haalat mein) aur sawab ke liye rakhey , uske guzishta sab gunah maaf kar diye jaeingey aur jisne lailatul-Qadr ka qiyam eman ke sath aur sawab ke liye kya to uske guzishta sarey gunah maaf kar diye jaeingey."
1782,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs lailatul-Qadr ka qiyam karega aur usko pa lega. mera khayal hai aap ne farmaya, eman ke aalem mein aur ehtisaab ke liye, usey bakhsh diya jaeyga."
1783,"Imam Malik (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Urwa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik raat masjid mein Namaz padhi to kuchh aur logon ne (bhi) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi, phir aap ne us se agli raat Namaz padhi to logon (ki tadaad ( mein izafa ho gaya, phir teesri ya chothi raat log jama huey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) nikal kar unke paas tashrif na laey. jab subah hui to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo tum ne kya maine dekha, mujhey tumharey paas aaney se iske siwa kisi cheez ne nahi rokaa ke mujhey dar hua ke kahin ye (namaz ( tum par farz na ho jaey. (Urwa ya unke baad ke kisi rawi ne) kaha : aur ye Ramazan mein hua."
1784,"Younus-bin-Yazeed ne ibne-Shahab se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne bataya ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ke waqt mein (ghar se) nikley aur masjid mein Namaz padhi, kuchh logon ne (bhi) aap ki Namaz ke sath Namaz ada ki, subah ko logon ne us barey mein baat cheet ki, chunanche (doosri raat ( log pahley se zyada jama ho gaey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dusri raat bhi bahar tashrif laey aur logon ne aap ki Namaz ke sath (iqtida (pairvi) mein) Namaz padhi, subah iska tazkira kartey rahe, teesri raat masjid mein aaney waley aur zyada ho gaey aap bahar tashrif laey aur logon ne aap ki Namaz ke sath Namaz padhi, jab chothi raat hui to masjid namaziyon ke liye tang ho gaee, aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) nikal kar unke paas tashrif na laaey, to unmein se kuchh logon ne Namaz , Namaz pukaarnaa shuru kar diya. lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar unke paas tashrif na laey yahan tak ke aap subah ki Namaz ke liye tashrif laey. jab subah ki Namaz poori kar li to logon ki taraf mutwajjeh huey, phir shahaadatein padh kar (ye khutbey ka hissa hain) farmaya : amaa-baad ! waqia ye hai ke aaj raat tumhara haal mujh se makhfi (chupaa) na tha lekin mujhey khadsha (khatraa) hua ke raat ki Namaz tum par farz na kar di jaey phir tum us (ki adaaeygi ( se aajiz raho."
1785,"Auzai ne kaha : mujh se Abda (bin-abi-Lubaba) ne zirr-(bin-jaish) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Ubai-ibne-Ka'b (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they jabke unse kaha gaya ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : jisne saal bhar qiyam kya usne shabe-qadr ko pa liya to ubaii (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha is Allah ki qism jiske siwa koi maabood nahi ! wo raat Ramazan mein hai. wo baghair kisi istisnaa ke Halaf uthatey they. aur Allah ki qism ! main khub janta hun ke wo raat kon si hai, ye wahi raat hai jis mein qiyam ka hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya tha, ye sattaiswin subah ki raat hai aur uski alamat ye hai ke us din ki subah ko suraj safaid tuloo hota hai, uski koi shuaa (kiran) nahi hoti."
1786,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : ham se Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Abda-bin-abi-Lubaba ko zirr-bin-habeesh se hadis bayan kartey huey suna, unhon-ne Hazrat Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, (zirr ne) kaha : Hazrat Ubai-ibne-Ka'b (Raziallahu anhu) ne lailatul-Qadr ke barey mein kaha : Allah ki qism ! main iske barey mein janta hun aur mera ghalib guman hai ke ye wahi raat hai jiske qiyam ka hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya tha, ye sattaiswin raat hai. Shoba ne, ''ye wahi raat hai jiske qiyam ka hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein hukm diya tha.''  is baat ke barey mein shak kiya, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey ye riwayat mere sathi ne un ( Abda-bin-abi-Lubaba ke hawale) se sunai thi."
1787,(Ubaidullah ke walid) Muaz ne kaha : ham se Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath pichhli riwayat ki manind (tarah) hadis bayan ki lekin usmein (Shoba ne iske barey mein shak kya) aur uske baad ki ibaarat bayan nahi ki.
1788,"Salma-bin-kuheil ne Kureb se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine aik raat apni khala Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan guzari , Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ko uthey aur apni zarurat (ki jagah ( aaey, phir apna chehra aur donon hath dhoey , phir so gaey phir uthey aur mishkeezey ke paas aaey aur iska bandhan khola , phir do (tarah ke) wuzu (bahut halka wuzu aur bahut zyada wuzu) ke darmyan ka wuzu kiya aur (pani) zyada (istemal) nahi kiya aur) wuzu ( achi tarah kiya, phir uthey aur Namaz shuru ki to main utha aur maine angdaaii li, is dar se ke aap ye na samjhein ke main aap (ke halaat jaanney ( ki khaatir jaag raha tha, phir maine wuzu kya, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur Namaz padhi. to main aap ki baain taraf khada ho gaya, aap ne mera hath pakda aur mujhey ghumaa kar apni daain taraf ( khada ( kar liya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki teraah (13) rakaat raat ki Namaz mukammal hui, phir aap let gaey aur so gaey yahan tak ke aap ki saans leney ki awaz aaney lagi , aap jab sotey they, to awaz aati thi. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) aaey, aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Namaz ki itlaa di, aap ne Namaz padhi ( sunnat fajr ada kiin (aur wuzu na kiya aur aap ki dua mein tha : aey Allah ! mairen dil mein noor daal de aur meri aankhon mein aur mere kanon mein noor bhar de aur meri daain taraf noor kar de aur meri baain taraf noor kar de aur mere uper noor kar de aur mere nichey noor kar de aur mere aagey aur mere peechhey noor kar de aur mere liye noor ko azeem kar de. (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke shagird ( Kureb ne bataya ke (unke ilawa mazeed ( saat (7) ( chizon ke barey mein dua mangi jin (ka talluq jism ke sandooq ( pasliyon aur ird-gird ke hissey ( se hai, meri mulaqat Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke betey se hui to unhon-ne mujhey unke barey mein bataya , unhon-ne bataya ke mere putthon , mere gosht , mere khoon , mere baalon aur meri khaal (ko noor kar de) , do aur bhi cheezein bataein ."
1789,"Imam Malik ne Makhrima-bin-Sulaiman se aur unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke Maula Kureb se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke unhon-ne aik raat Ummul-Momenin Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan guzari jo unki khala thin, to main sarhaaney ( bistar (ke arz mein leta aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ki ahliya us ( bistar (ke tool ( lambai ( mein letey , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) so gaey yahan tak ke raat aadhi hui. ya us se thoda pahley ya thoda baad ka waqt hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bedaar ho gaey aur apne hath ke sath apne chehrey se neend zaayel karne lagey, ( chehrey par hath phera ( phir aap ne sura aale Imran ki aakhiri das aayatein tilawat farmaein , phir aap uth kar ek latkey huey mishkeezey ke paas gaey aur us se wuzu kya aur achi tarah wuzu kya, phir khadey huey aur Namaz padhney lagey. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main utha aur maine bhi wahi kya jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya tha. phir ja kar aap ke pahlu mein khada ho gaya is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna daaiyaan hath mere sar par rakha aur mere daain kaan ko pakad kar) aahista se) modney lagey. phir aap ne do rakaat Namaz padhi. phir do rakatein , phir do rakatein , phir do rakatein , phir do rakatein , phir do rakatein padhiin. phir witr padha , phir aap let gaey yahan tak ke muazzan aap ke paas aaya to aap khadey huey aur do halki rakatein padhiin , phir tashrif le gaey aur subah ki Namaz ada ki."
1790,"ayaaz-bin-Abdullah fihrii ne Makhrima-bin-Sulaiman se isi sanad ke sath yahi riwayat bayan ki aur ye izafa kya : phir aap ne pani ke aik puraaney mishkeezey ka rukh kya, phir miswak ki aur wuzu kya aur achi tarah wuzu kya, lekin pani bahut hi kam bahaya , phir mujhey hilaayaa aur main khada ho gaya. padhi. baqi saari hadis Malik ki hadis ki tarah hai."
1791,"Amr ne abde-rabba-bin-Saeed se, unhon-ne Makhrima-bin-Sulaiman se, unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke Maula Kureb se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : main Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan soyaa aur us raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein ke paas they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kiya, phir khadey huey aur Namaz padhney lagey, mein aap ki baain taraf khada ho gaya to aap ne mujhey pakad kar apni daain taraf kar liya. us raat aap ne teraah (13) rakatein padhiin. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) so gaey yahan tak ke aap (ke saanson ( ki awaz aaney lagi , jab aap sotey to saans leney ki awaz aati thi. phir aap ke paas muazzan aaya to aap bahar tashrif le gaey aur Namaz ada ki, aap ne (nai sire se) wuzu nahi kya. Amr ne kaha maine ye hadis Bukair-bin-Ashajj ko sunai to unhon-ne kaha : Kureb ne mujhey yahi hadis sunai thi."
1792,"Zuhak ne Makhrima-bin-Sulaiman se, unhon-ne Kureb Maula Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine aik raat apni khala Memuna binte Haris (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan Basar ki, maine unse arz ki. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uthein to aap mujhey bhi bedaar kar dein. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz ke liye khadey huey to main aap ki baain taraf khada ho gaya. aap ne mera hath pakda aur mujhey apni daain taraf mein kar diya, jab mujhey jhapkii aaney lagti to aap mere kaan ki lo pakad letey , aap ne gyara (11) rakatein padhein , phir aap ne kamar aur pindliyon ke gird kapda lapet kar usey sahara bana liya (aur so gaey ( yahan tak ke main aap ke soney ki haalat mein aap ke saans leney ki awaz sun raha tha. to jab aap ke samney subah zahir hui to aap ne halki do rakatein padhiin."
1793,"Sufiyan ne Amr-bin-Dinar se, unhon-ne Kureb Maula Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne apni khala Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan raat Basar ki. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ke waqt uthey , phir aap ne latkii hui mashk se halka wuzu kiya ( Kureb ne) kaha : unhon (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne aap ke wuzu ki kaifiyat bayan ki aur wuzu ko halka aur kam kartey rahe, Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main utha aur wahi kya jo Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya. phir aa kar main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baain taraf khada ho gaya, aap ne mujhey apne peechhey kya (aur ghumaa kar) apni daain taraf kar liya. phir aap ne Namaz padhi. phir let kar so gaey yahan tak ke aawaz se saans leney lagey. phir Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) aaey aur aapko Namaz ki itlaa di, aap bahar tashrif le gaey aur subah ki Namaz ada farmai aur) nayaa ( wuzu na kiya. Sufiyan ne kaha : ye ( neend ke bawajud wuzu ki zarurat na hona ( Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka khaassa tha kyonke ham tak ye baat pahunchi hai ke aap ki aankhen soti thin dil nahi sotaa tha."
1794,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ( ghandar ( ne kaha : ham se Shoba ne Salma se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Kureb se aur unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine apni khala Memuna ke yahan raat guzari , maine ( wahan reh kar) mushaahida kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kaisey Namaz padhtey hain. kaha : aap uthey , peshab kya, phir apna chehra aur hatheliyan dhoein . phir so gaey. aap ( kuchh der baad) phir uthey , mishkeezey ke paas gaey aur iska bandhan khola , phir lagan ya pyaley mein pani undela aur usko apne hath se jhukaya , phir do wuzuon ke darmyan ka khoobsurat wuzu kiya ( wuzu na bahut halka kiya aur na usmein mubaalgha kiya lekin achi tarah kiya ( , phir uth kar Namaz padhney lagey, mein aap ke pahlu mein kharaa ho gaya, aap ki baain taraf khatraa hua. kaha : to aap ne mujhey pakad kar apni daain taraf kar diya, aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki teraah (13) rakaat Namaz mukammal hui, phir aap so gaey yahan tak ke saanson ki awaz aaney lagi aur jab aap so jatey to ham aap ke soney ko aap ke saans ki awaz se pehchantey , phir aap Namaz ke liye bahar tashrif laey aur Namaz ada ki. aur aap apni Namaz ya apne sajdey mein ye dua maangney lagey : aey Allah ! mere dil mein noor paida kar aur mere kanon mein noor paida kar aur meri aankhon mein noor paida kar aur mere daain noor bana aur mere baain noor paida farma aur mere aagey aur mere peechhey noor kar aur mere uper noor kar aur mere liye noor bana.     .....  ya farmaya : mujhey noor bana."
1795,"Nazar-bin-Shumail ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne khabar di, kaha : hamein Salma-bin-kuheil ne Bukair se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Kureb se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki. Salma ne kaha : main Kureb ko mila to unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : main apni khala Memuna ke yahan tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey. padhi. phir unhon-ne ghandar ( Muhammad-bin-Jafar ( ki hadis (1794) ki tarah bayan kya aur kaha : aur mujhey saraapaa noor kar de aur unhon-ne ( kisi baat mein) shak ka izhar na kiya."
1796,"Saeed-bin-Masruq ne Salma-bin-kuheil se, unhon-ne abu Rushdain ( Kureb ( Maula Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine apni khala Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan raat guzari , phir hadis bayan ki lekin usmein chehrey aur hatheliyan dhoney ka zikr nahi hai, haan , ye kaha : phir aap mashk ke paas aaey, iska bandhan khola , aur do wuzuon ke darmyan ka wuzu kiya phir bistar par aaey aur so gaey phir aap dobara uthey aur mashk ke paas aaey, iska bandhan khola , phir dobara wuzu kya jo ( sahi mana mein) wuzu tha aur kaha : mera noor azeem kar de aur ye riwayat nahi kya ke mujhey saraapaa noor kar de."
1797,"Aqeel-bin-Khalid se riwayat hai ke Salma-bin-kuheil ne un ( Aqeel ( se hadis bayan ki ke Kureb ne un (Salma ( se hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas guzari , unhon (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uth kar mishkeezey ke paas gaey aur is mein se pani undela aur wuzu kya aur aap ne na pani zyada istemal kya na wuzu mein koi kami ki. aur poori hadis bayan ki aur is mein ye bhi hai ke aap ne us raat unnees kalimaat par mushtamil dua ki. ( tamam alfaz jama karein to unnees bantey hain) Salma ne kaha : Kureb ne wo kalimaat mujhey bataaey they aur main unmein se baara kalimaat ko yad rakh saka aur baqi bhool gaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Allah ! mere dil mein noor paida farma aur meri zaban mein noor paida farma aur mere kaan mein noor paida farma aur meri aankh mein noor paida farma aur mere uper noor kar de aur mere nichey noor kar de aur mere daain noor kar de aur mere baain noor kar de aur mere aagey noor kar de aur mere peechhey noor kar de aur mere andar noor kar de aur mere noor ko azeem kar de."
1798,"Sharik-bin-abi nameer ne Kureb se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main aik raat Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar soyaa , jabke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke yahaan they taake main dekhun ke raat ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz ki kaifiyat kya hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh waqt apne ghar walon ke sath guftgu farmai, phir aap so gaey. padhi. aagey poori hadis bayan ki aur is mein ye bhi tha ke phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uthey , wuzu kiya aur miswak ki."
1799,"Habib-bin-abi-Sabit ne Muhammad-bin Ali-bin-Abdullah-bin-Abbas se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke wo (eik raat ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan soey to (raat ko) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jaagey , miswak ki aur wuzu farmaya aur aap (us waqt) ye aayatein mubaraka padh rahe they : ''yaqeenan aasmanon aur zamin ki takhleeq mein aur din raat ke aane-jaane mein khalis aql rakhney walon ke liye nishaniyan hain.'' ye aayatein tilawat farmaein (suraa aale imraan,aayet-190-200) yahan tak ke sura khatm ki, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur do rakatein padhiin, unmein bahut lamba qiyam , rukoo aur sajdey kiye, phir wapas paltey aur so gaey yahan tak ke aap ke saans ki awaz sunai dene lagi , phir aap ne is tarah teen baar kya, chh rakatein padhein , har baar aap miswak kartey, wuzu farmatey aur un aayaat ko tilawat farmatey, phir aap ne teen witr padhey , phir muazzan ne azan di to aap Namaz ke liye bahar tashrif le gaey aur aap ye dua kar rahe they : aey Allah ! mere dil mein noor kar de aur meri zaban mein noor kar de aur meri sama'at mein noor kar de aur meri aankh mein noor kar de aur mere peechhey noor kar de aur mere aagey noor kar de aur mere uper noor kar de aur mere nichey noor kar de, aey Allah ! mujhey noor inayat farmaa."
1800,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha, mujhey Ata ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : maine aik raat apni khala Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke paas Basar ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ki nafl Namaz padhney ke liye jaagey . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uth kar mashk ki taraf gaey aur wuzu farmaya, phir khadey ho kar Namaz padhi, jab maine aapko ye kartey dekha to main bhi utha aur maine bhi mashk se wuzu kiya , (jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wuzu kartey rahe, Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) jaagney ke baad ghaur se unhein dekhtey rahe taake aap ki ittaba (pairvi) kar sakein) phir main aap ke baain pahlu mein khada ho gaya to aap ne apni pusht ke peechhey se mera hath pakda , isi tarah peechhey se mujhey daain taraf theek karke khada kya. (ata ne kaha :) maine puchha : kya ye nafl Namaz mein hua tha? unhon-ne kaha : haan."
1801,"Qais-bin-Sad, Ata se hadis bayan kartey hain, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas bheja Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) meri khala Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar mein they, to wo raat maine aap ke sath guzari , aap raat ko uth kar Namaz padhney lagey aur main aap ke baain taraf khada ho gaya to aap ne mujhey apni pusht ke peechhey se pakda aur apni daain taraf kar liya. (is hadis mein mazeed ye tafseel samney aai ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko unke walid ne bheja tha.)"
1802,Abdul-Malik ne Ata se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : maine apni khala Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan raat guzari . aagey ibne-Juraij aur Qais-bin-Sad ki riwayat ki tarah hai.
1803,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ibne-Musanna  aur ibne-Bashar ne ghandar , Shoba aur abu-Jamra ki sanad se hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ko teraah (13) rakatein padha kartey they ( yahi raat ki rakaton ki zyada se zyada tadaad hai jis mein do khafeef (choti) rakatein shamil hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka mamool (routine) gyara (11) ka tha jis tarah Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya)."
1804,"Hazrat Zaid-bin-Khalid Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, ke unhon-ne (dil mein) kaha : main aaj raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz ka ( gehri nazar se) mushaahida karunga, to ( maine dekha ke) aap ne do halki rakatein padhiin , phir do intihai lambi rakatein bahut hi zyada lambi rakatein ada kin, phir do rakatein padhein. jo (un lambi-tareen) rakaton se halki thin, phir do rakatein padhiin jo apne se pahley ki do rakaton se halki thin, phir do rakatein padhiin jo apne se pahley ki do rakaton se kam tar thin, phir do rakatein padhiin jo apne se pehli wali rakaton se kam thin, phir witr padha to ye teraah (13) rakatein huin."
1805,"Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : main aik safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath tha, ham pani ke aik ghaat par pahunchey to aap ne farmaya : Jaabir ! kya tum sawari ko pilaaney ke liye ghaat par nahi utro gey ? maine kaha : kyon nahi ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( bhi) ghaat par utrey aur main bhi utra , phir aap zarurat ke liye tashrif le gaey aur maine aap ke liye wuzu ka pani rakh diya, aap wapas aaey aur wuzu farmaya, phir aap khadey huey aur aik kapdey mein Namaz padhi jiske donon kinarey aap ne mukhalif samton (dishaaon) mein daal rakhey they (daain kinarey ko baain kandhey par aur baain kinarey ko daain kandhey par daala) mein aap ke peechhey khada ho gaya to aap ne mere kaan se pakad kar mujhey apni daain taraf kar liya."
1806,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab raat ko Namaz padhney ke liye uthtey , apni Namaz ka shuruat do halki rakaton se farmatey."
1807,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi raat ko (namaz ke liye) uthey to wo apni Namaz ki shuruat do halki rakaton se kare.
1808,"Imam Malik (Reh.) ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Taaus se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab raat ki aa-khirii tehai mein Namaz ke liye uthtey to farmatey : aey Allah ! tamam tareef terey hi liye hai, to aasmanon aur zamin ka noor hai aur terey hi liye hamd hai to aasmanon aur zamin ko qaaim rakhney wala hai aur terey hi liye hamd hai to aasmanon aur zamin ka aur jo kuchh unmein hai to paalne wala hai. aur to bar-haq hai aur tera wada sachcha hai aur tera qaul atal hai aur terey sath mulaqat qataii hai aur jannat haq hai aur jahannam haq hai aur qiyamat haq hai. aey Allah maine apne aapko terey sipurd kar diya aur main tujh par eman laya aur maine tujh par twakkul aur bharosa kiya aur teri taraf rujoo kiya aur teri taufeeq se (terey munkiron se) jhagdaa kiya aur terey hi huzoor faisla laya ( tujhey hi Hakim taslim kiya ( to bakhsh de wo gunah jo maine pahley kiye aur jo baad mein kiye aur jo chhup kar kiye aur jo zaahiran kiye tu hi mera maabood hai terey siwa koi maabood nahi."
1809,"Sufiyan aur ibne-Juraij donon ne Sulaiman ahwal se, unhon-ne Taaus se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki. ibne-Juraij aur Imam Malik (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ki ( guzishta ( hadis ke alfaz aik jaisey hain, do jumlon ke siwa koi ikhtilaf nahi, ibne-Juraij ne qiyam ke bajaey ( qaiyim ( kaha ( mana aik hain) aur (واسررت) ki jagah (وما اسررت) kaha, (Sufiyan) ibne-Uena ki hadis mein kuchh izafa hai, wo bahut si jumlon mein Imam Malik (Rahmatullahi-alaih) aur ibne-Juraij se ikhtilaf kartey hain."
1810,"Qais-bin-Sad ne Taaus se, unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi hadis riwayat ki. (is hadis ke rawi Imran-al-qaseer) alfaz un (Imam Malik, Sufiyan, ibne-Juraij) ke alfaz se miltey-jultey hain."
1811,"abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne kaha : maine Ummul-Momenin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab raat ko Namaz ke liye uthtey they, to kis cheez ke sath Namaz ki shuruat kartey they? unhon-ne jawab diya : jab aap raat ko uthtey to Namaz ka aa-ghaaz (is dua se) kartey : aey Allah ! Jibraeel , Mikaail aur Israafeel ke rab! aasmanon aur zamin ko paida farmaney waley ! posheeda aur zahir ko jaanney waley ! terey bandey jin baton mein ikhtilaf kartey they, tu hi unke darmiyan faisla farmaeyga. jin baton mein ikhtilaf kya gaya hai tu hi apne hukm se mujhey unmein se jo haq hai is par chala , be-shak tu hi jisey chahey seedhi raah par chalaataa hai."
1812,"Yusuf maajishoon ne kaha : mujh se mere walid (Yaqoob-bin-abi-Salma maajishoon) ne Abdur-Rehman Aaraj se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ubaidullah-bin-abi-Raafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz ke liye khadey hotey they, to farmatey :  وَجَّهْتُ وَجْهِيَ لِلَّذِي فَطَرَ السَّمَاوَاتِ وَالْأَرْضَ حَنِيفًا وَمَا أَنَا مِنْ الْمُشْرِكِينَ إِنَّ صَلَاتِي وَنُسُكِي وَمَحْيَايَ وَمَمَاتِي لِلَّهِ رَبِّ الْعَالَمِينَ لَا شَرِيكَ لَهُ وَبِذَلِكَ أُمِرْتُ وَأَنَا مِنْ الْمُسْلِمِينَ اللَّهُمَّ أَنْتَ الْمَلِكُ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا أَنْتَ أَنْتَ رَبِّي وَأَنَا عَبْدُكَ ظَلَمْتُ نَفْسِي وَاعْتَرَفْتُ بِذَنْبِي فَاغْفِرْ لِي ذُنُوبِي جَمِيعًا إِنَّهُ لَا يَغْفِرُ الذُّنُوبَ إِلَّا أَنْتَ وَاهْدِنِي لِأَحْسَنِ الْأَخْلَاقِ لَا يَهْدِي لِأَحْسَنِهَا إِلَّا أَنْتَ وَاصْرِفْ عَنِّي سَيِّئَهَا لَا يَصْرِفُ عَنِّي سَيِّئَهَا إِلَّا أَنْتَ لَبَّيْكَ وَسَعْدَيْكَ وَالْخَيْرُ كُلُّهُ فِي يَدَيْكَ وَالشَّرُّ لَيْسَ إِلَيْكَ أَنَا بِكَ وَإِلَيْكَ تَبَارَكْتَ وَتَعَالَيْتَ أَسْتَغْفِرُكَ وَأَتُوبُ إِلَيْكَ                                                                                 ''maine apna rukh us zaat ki taraf kar diya hai. jisne aasmanon aur zamin ko paida farmaya, har taraf se yaksoo ho kar, aur main iske sath Sharik thahraaney walon mein se nahi, meri Namaz aur meri har (badanii w maalii) ibadat aur mera jeenaa aur mera marnaa Allah ke liye hai jo kaaynaat ka rab hai, iska koi Sharik nahi aur usi ka mujhey hukm mila hai aur main farmaanbardaarii karne walon mein se hun. aey Allah ! tu hi badshah hai terey siwa koi bandagii ke laaiq nahi, to mera rab hai main tera banda hon aur maine apne uper zulm kya hai aur apne gunah ka aetraaf kiya hai, isliye mere sarey gunah bakhsh de kyonke gunahon ko bakhshney wala terey siwa koi nahi, aur meri behtreen akhlaq ki taraf rehnumai farma, terey siwa behtreen akhlaq ki raah par chalaney wala koi nahi, aur burey akhlaq mujh se hata de, terey siwa burey akhlaq ko mujh se door karne wala koi nahi, main terey huzoor hazir hun aur donon jahaanon ki sa'adatein (khushiyan) tujh se hain har tarah ki bhalai terey hath mein hai aur burai ka teri taraf koi guzar nahi hai main terey hi sahaarey hon, aur teri hi taraf mera rukh hai, to barkat wala, rafa't wala aur bulandi wala hai main tujh se bakhshish mangta hun aur terey huzoor tauba karta hun.'' aur jab aap rukoo kartey to farmatey :                                                                                      اللَّهُمَّ لَكَ رَكَعْتُ وَبِكَ آمَنْتُ وَلَكَ أَسْلَمْتُ خَشَعَ لَكَ سَمْعِي وَبَصَرِي وَمُخِّي وَعَظْمِي وَعَصَبِي                                                          ''aey Allah ! main terey samney jhukaa hua hun aur main tujh hi par eman laya hon, apne aapko terey hi sipurd kar diya hai, mere kaan aur meri aankhen aur mera maghz aur meri haddiyaan aur meri ragein aur mere patthey terey hi huzoor jhukey huey hain.'' aur jab rukoo se uthtey to kehtey :            اللَّهُمَّ رَبَّنَا لَكَ الْحَمْدُ مِلْءَ السَّمَاوَاتِ وَمِلْءَ الْأَرْضِ وَمِلْءَ مَا بَيْنَهُمَا وَمِلْءَ مَا شِئْتَ مِنْ شَيْءٍ بَعْدُ                                                     ''aey Allah ! hamarey rab , terey hi liye hamd hai jis se aasamaanon aur zamin ki wus'atein bhar jayen aur uske baad jo to chahey uski wus'atein bhar jaaein.'' aur jab aap sajda kartey to kehtey :       اللَّهُمَّ لَكَ سَجَدْتُ وَبِكَ آمَنْتُ وَلَكَ أَسْلَمْتُ سَجَدَ وَجْهِي لِلَّذِي خَلَقَهُ وَصَوَّرَهُ وَشَقَّ سَمْعَهُ وَبَصَرَهُ تَبَارَكَ اللَّهُ أَحْسَنُ الْخَالِقِينَ ثُمَّ يَكُونُ                 ''aey Allah ! maine terey hi huzoor sajda kiya aur tujh hi par eman laya aur apne aapko terey hi hawale kiya, mera chehra us zaat ke samney sajda rez hai jisne usey paida kiya, uski sura banai aur uske kaan aur uski aankhen taraashein, barkat wala hai Allah jo behtreen khaaliq hai.'' phir tashahud aur salam ke darmyan mein ye dua padhtey:                                                                                             اللَّهُمَّ اغْفِرْ لِي مَا قَدَّمْتُ وَمَا أَخَّرْتُ وَمَا أَسْرَرْتُ وَمَا أَعْلَنْتُ وَمَا أَسْرَفْتُ وَمَا أَنْتَ أَعْلَمُ بِهِ مِنِّي أَنْتَ الْمُقَدِّمُ وَأَنْتَ الْمُؤَخِّرُ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا أَنْتَ''aey Allah ! bakhsh de jo khataein maine pahley kiin ya baad mein kiin aur chipa kar kiin ya ailaaniya kiin aur jo bhi zyadti maine ki aur jiska mujh se zyada tumhen ilm hai. ( itaat aur khair mein) tu hi aagey karne wala hai aur tu hi peechhey karne wala hai aur terey siwa koi ibadat ka haqdaar nahi.''"
1813,"Abdul-Azeez-bin-Abdullah-bin-abi Salma ne apne chacha Maajishoon (Yaqoob )-bin-abi Salma se aur unhon-ne ( Abdur-Rehman ( Aaraj se isi sanad ke sath yahi hadis bayan ki aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Namaz ki shuruat farmatey to Allahu-akbar kehtey, phir dua padhtey : (وجهت وجهيي) usmein ((انا من المسلمین (ke bajaey)           (و انا اول المسلمين) aur main itaat w farmaan-bardaarii mein awwaleen (maqam par faaiz) hon ke alfaz hain. aur kaha : jab aap rukoo se apna sar uthatey to ((sami-allahu-liman-hamida; rabbana-wa-lakal-hamd) ( سمع الله لمن حمده ربنا ولك الحمد )) kehtey aur (saw-ra-hu) ( uski sura giri ki) ke baad) f-ahsin sura ( ) usko behtreen shakl w sura inayat farmai) ke alfaz kahey aur kaha jab salam phertey to kehtey : ((Allahumagfirli-ma-qaddamet) (اللهم اغفرلي ما قدمت)) aey Allah ! bakhsh de jo maine pahley kiya. hadis ke aakhir tak aur unhon-ne tashahud aur salam pherney ke darmyan ke alfaz nahi kahey."
1814,"Abdullah-bin-Numair , abu-Muawiya aur Jarir sab ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Sad-bin-ubaida se, unhon-ne mustaurid-bin-ahnaf se, unhon-ne sila-bin-zufr se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, . unhon-ne kaha : aik raat maine Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi, aap ne sura Baqra ki shuruat farmaii, maine (dil mein) kaha : aap so aayatein padh kar rukoo farmaaengey magar aap aagey badh gaey maine kaha : aap usey (poori) rakaat mein padhengey , aap aagey padhtey gaey, maine sochaa , usey padh kar rukoo karengey magar aap ne sura Nisa shuru kar di, aap ne wo poori padhi, phir aap ne aale-Imran shuru kar di, usko pura padha , aap thahar-thahar kar qirat farmatey rahe jab aisi aayat se guzartey jis mein tasbeeh hai to ( Subhan-Allah ( kehtey aur jab sawal (karne wali aayat) se guzartey (padhtey) to sawal kartey aur jab panah maangney wali aayat se guzartey to. (Allah se) panah maangtey, phir aap ne rukoo farmaya aur ((subhana-rabbi-yal-azeem) ( سبحان ربي العظيم )) kehney lagey, aap ka rukoo (taqriban) aap ke qiyam jitna tha. phir aap ne((sami-allahu-liman-hamida) (سمع الله لمن حمده)) kaha : phir aap lambi der khadey rahe, taqriban itni der jitni der rukoo kiya tha, phir sajda kiya aur ((subhana-rabbi-yal-a'laa) (سبحان ربي الاعلي )) kehney lagey. aur aap ka sajda (bhi) aap ke qiyam ke qareeb tha. Jarir ki riwayat mein ye izafa hai ke aap ne kaha : ((sami-allahu-liman-hamida; rabbana-lakal-hamd) ( سمع الله لمن حمده ربنا لك الحمد )) yani ((rabbana-lakal-hamd) (ربنا لك الحمد)) ka izafa hai.)"
1815,Jarir ne Aamash se aur unhon-ne abu-Waeil se riwayat ki. unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi aap ne itni lambi Namaz padhi ke maine aik na-pasandida kaam ka irada kar liya. kaha : to unse puchha gaya aap ne kis baat ka irada kya tha? unhon-ne kaha : maine irada kiya ke baith jaun aur aapko (akeley hi qiyam ki haalat mein) chhod dun.
1816,Ali-bin-Mus'hir ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
1817,Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney aik aisey aadmi ka zikr kiya gaya jo raat bhar soyaa raha yahan tak ke subah ho gaee aap ne farmaya : wo (aisa) shakhs hai ke shaitan ne uske kaan mein. ya farmaya : uske donon kanon mein peshab kar diya hai.
1818,Hazrat Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne raat ke waqt unhein aur Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko jagaaya aur farmaya : kya tum log Namaz nahi padhogey? maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! hamari jaanein Allah ke hath mein hain jab wo hamein uthana chahta hai utha deta hai jab maine aap se ye kaha to aap wapas chaley gaey phir maine aapko suna ke aap wapas palat-tey huey apni raan par hath maartey they aur kehtey (aayat ka aik tukda padhtey) they : insan sabse badh kar jhagda karne wala hai (jadl (jhagda) ye thi ke jagaey janey par mamnoon honey aur Namaz padhney ki bajaey uzr pesh kya gaya. (
1819,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne ye farman Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf mansub kya aap ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi so jata hai to shaitan iske sar ke pichhley hissey par teen girhein lagata hai har girah par thapki deta hai ke tum par aik bahut lambi raat (ka sona lazim ( hai jab insan bedaar ho kar Allah Taala ka zikr karta hai to aik girah khul jati hai aur jab wo wuzu karta hai us se 2 girhein khul jati hain phir jab Namaz padhta hai saari girhein khul jati hain aur wo chaaq chauband hashshaash bashshaash paak tabeeat (ke saath) subah karta hai warna ( jaag kar ibadat nahi karta to ( subah ko gandey dil ke sath aur sust uthtaa hai.
1820,"Ubaidullah ne kaha : mujhey Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kya unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : kuchh namazein ghar mein padha karo aur un ( gharon ( ko qabrein na banao ."
1821,"Ayub ne Naafe se unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : gharon main ( nafl ( namazein padho aur unhein qabrein na banao ."
1822,Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi apni masjid mein Namaz ( ba-jamaat ( ada kar ley to apni Namaz mein se apne ghar ke liye bhi kuchh hissey rakhey kyonke Allah iske ghar mein iske Namaz padhney ki wjah se khair w bhalai rakhega.
1823,Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is ghar ki misal jis mein Allah ka zikr kya jata hai aur us ghar ki misal jis mein Allah ko yad nahi kya jata zinda aur murda jaisi hai.
1824,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : apne gharon ko qabristaan na banao shaitan us ghar se bhagta hai jis mein sura Baqra padhi jati hai.
1825,"Abdullah Saeed ne kaha : Umar-bin Ubaidullah ke aazad karda ghulam Salim abu-Nazar ne hamein Basar-bin-Saeed se hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne Hazrat Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chatai ka aik chhota sa hujra banwaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( ghar se) bahar aa kar usmein Namaz padhney lagey log us ( hujrey ( tak aap ke peechhey peechhey aaey aur aa kar aap ki iqtida (pairvi) mein Namaz padhney lagey, phir aik aur raat log aaey aur) hujrey ke) paas aagey jabke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke paas aaney mein taakheer kar di. kaha : aap unke paas tashrif na laey sahaba kiram (rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne apni aawaazein buland kin (taake aap aawaazein sun kar tashrif ley aaein (aur darwazey par chhoti-chhoti kankariyan maarein to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghussey ki haalat mein unki taraf tashrif laey aur unse farmaya : tum musalsal ye amal kartey rahe yahan tak ke mujhey khayal hua ke ye Namaz tum par lazim qarar de di jaeygi, isliye tum apne gharon mein Namaz padha karo kyonke insan ki farz Namaz ke siwa wahi behtar hai jo ghar mein padhey."
1826,"Musa-bin-Aqba ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine abu-Nazar se suna unhon-ne Basar-bin-Saeed se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne masjid mein chatai se aik hujra banwaya aur aap ne usmein chand raatein Namaz padhi yahan tak ke aap ke paas log jama ho gaey. phir uper zikr ki gaee riwayat bayan ki aur is mein ye izafa kya ke (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ( agar tum par Namaz farz kar di gaee to tum (sab) uski pabandi nahi kar sakogey. (ye hujra aetikaf ke liye tha.)"
1827,Saeed bin abi Saeed ne abu-Salma (bin Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf ( se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aik chatai thi aap raat ko us se hujra bana letey aur is mein Namaz padhtey to logon ne bhi aap ki iqtida (pairvi) mein Namaz padhni shuru kar di aap din ke waqt usey bichha letey they aik raat log kasarat ke sath jama ho gaey to aap ne farmaya : logo ! itney aamaal ki pabandi karo jitney aamaal ki tum mein taqat hai kyonke (is waqt tak) Allah Taala ( ajr w sawab dene se) nahi uktaataa yahan tak ke tum khud uktaa jao aur yaqinan Allah ke nazdeek zyada mahboob amal wahi hai jis par hameshgi ikhtiyar ki jaey chahey wo kam ho. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghar waley jab koi amal kartey to usey hamesha barqarar rakhtey.
1828,"Sad bin Ibrahim se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne abu-Salma se suna, wo Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se hadis bayan kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya : Allah Taala ko kon sa amal zyada pasand hai? aap ne farmaya : jisey hamesha kya jaey agarche kam ho."
1829,Alqama se riwayat hai kaha maine Ummul-Momenin ! Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se sawal kya aur kaha Ummul-Momenin ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke amal ki kaifiyat kya thi? kya aap ( kisi khas amal ke liye) kuchh din makhsoos farma letey they? unhon-ne farmaya : nahi aap ka amal daaimi hota tha aur tum mein se kon is qadr istitaat rakhta hai jitni istitaat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mein thi?
1830,"Qasim-bin-Muhammad ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ke yahan mahboob tareen kaam wo hai jis par hamesha amal kya jaey bale hi wo thoda sa ho. (Qasim-bin-Muhammad ne) kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) jab koi amal kartin to usko lazim kar letin ."
1831,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : hamein ibne-Ulaih ne hadis sunai, neez Zuhair-bin-Harab ne kaha : hamein Ismail ne hadis sunai, un donon ( ibne-Ulaih aur Ismail) ne Abdul-Azeez bin Suheb se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein dakhil huey aur) dekha ke) 2 sutunon ke darmyan aik rassi latki hui hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : ye kya hai? sahaba kiram (rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne kaha : Hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ki rassi hai, wo Namaz padhti rehti hain, jab sust padti hain ya thak jati hain to usko pakad leti hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey khol do, har shakhs Namaz padhey jab tak khush aur taro-taza rahe, jab sust pad jaey ya thak jaey to baith jaey. Zuhair ki riwayat main ( قعد ( ki bajaey) ( فليقعد ( hai. yani maazi ki bajaey Amr ka seegha istemal kya, mafhoom aik hi hai."
1832,"Abdul-Waris ne Abdul-Azeez (bin Suheb ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
1833,"ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein bataya ke Haula binte- Tuvait bin Habib bin Asad bin abdul-Uzzaa is aalim mein unke qareeb se guzri jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke paas they, kaha : maine kaha : ye Haula binte- Tuvait hain aur logon ka khayal hai ke ye raat bhar nahi sotin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (kya (raat bhar nahi soti ! itna amal apnao jitney ki tum taqat rakhtey ho. Allah ki qism ! Allah nahi uktaaeyga yahan tak ke tum uktaa jao."
1834,"abu-Usama aur Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey mere walid ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kartey huey khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere paas tashrif laey aur mere paas aik khatun maujood thin, aap ne puchha : ye kon hai? maine kaha : ye aisi aurat hai jo raat bhar nahi soti , Namaz padhti rehti hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : itna amal karo jitna tumharey bas mein ho, Allah ki qism ! Allah nahi uktaaeyga yahan tak ke tum hi amal se uktaa jao . Allah ke yahan Deen ka wahi amal pasand hai jis par amal karne wala hameshgi kare. abu-Usama ki riwayat mein hai, ye banu-Asad ki aurat thi."
1835,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs Namaz mein oonghney lagey to wo so jaey yahan tak ke neend jati rahe kyonke jab tum mein se koi shakhs oongh ki haalat mein Namaz padhta hai to mumkin hai wo istighfar karne chaley lekin) uski bajaey) apne aapko bura bhala kehney lagey,"
1836,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke waastey bayan ki hain, phir unmein se kuchh hadisein zikr kin, unmein se ye bhi thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs raat ko qiyam karey aur uski zaban par qirat mushkil ho jaey aur usey pata na chaley ke wo kya keh raha hai to usey let jana chahiye."
